0After%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20being%20slammed%20against%20concrete%20and%20thrown%20about%2C%20the%20nickel-plated%20brass%20fittings%20held%20up%20well%2C%20with%20no%20warping%20or%20dents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20fit%20very%20securely%20and%20tightly%20on%20my%20water%20connection%2C%20and%20it%20had%20the%20fastest%20water%20flow%20of%20all%20the%20hose%20contenders%3A%2010.91%20gallons%20per%20minute.%20That%20makes%20it%20especially%20valuable%20for%20tasks%20like%20filling%20up%20a%20pool%20or%20large%20bucket.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20ground%20to%20water%2C%20the%20Dramm%20hose%20will%20make%20the%20chore%20go%20by%20quickly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20more%20expensive%20than%20the%20average%20hose%2C%20the%20investment%20is%20well%20worth%20it.%20Watering%20your%20garden%20or%20washing%20your%20car%20becomes%20significantly%20more%20pleasant%2C%20and%20you%20won't%20have%20to%20replace%20it%20because%20of%20hose%20body%20damage%20or%20frequent%20kinking.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20it%20comes%20in%20bright%20colors%20that%20make%20backyard%20chores%20a%20little%20more%20fun.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20find%20a%20cheap%20hose%20that%20doesn't%20compromise%20some%20features%2C%20be%20it%20durability%2C%20kink%20resistance%2C%20or%20weather%20resistance.%20For%20the%20most%20part%2C%20what%20you%20pay%20for%20is%20what%20you%20get%20in%20the%20hose%20department.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20one%20exception%3A%20the%20Continental%20hose.%20It's%20not%20dirt-cheap%2C%20but%20it%20is%20more%20affordable%20than%20all%20of%20our%20other%20picks%2C%20and%20it%20performs%20very%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%2050-ft%20rolled%20rubber%20black%20continental%20garden%20hose%20lying%20on%20the%20grass%2C%20best%20cheap%20hose%20of%202022%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60393145d9208800185923ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAt%20around%20%2450%2C%20the%20Continental%20Black%20Water%20Hose%20is%20a%20bit%20cheaper%20than%20other%20options%2C%20but%20still%20offers%20good%20durability.%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hose%20is%20heavy%2C%20rugged%2C%20and%20durable.%20It%20has%20a%20thick%20rubber%20body%20and%20strong%20solid%20brass%20fittings%20that%20held%20up%20to%20repeated%20attacks%20against%20concrete.%20Overall%2C%20it%20provides%20a%20smooth%20and%20relatively%20easy%20watering%20experience%20because%20it%20fits%20tightly%20over%20the%20water%20connection%20and%20doesn't%20kink%20or%20bend.%20The%20most%20difficult%20part%20is%20dragging%20around%20the%2012%20pounds%20of%20weight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20flow%20rate%20is%20pretty%20good%20%E2%80%94%C2%A08.57%20gallons%20per%20minute%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0which%20is%20a%20little%20slower%20than%20our%20top%20pick%2C%20the%20Dramm%20hose.%20While%20I'd%20say%20the%20two%20hoses%20are%20pretty%20comparable%2C%20the%20Continental%20is%20slightly%20thicker%20and%20less%20efficient%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20come%20in%20multiple%20colors%20(just%20black).%20That%20being%20said%2C%20these%20flaws%20aren't%20insurmountable%2C%20and%20I%20was%20still%20satisfied%20with%20this%20budget%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20expandable%5C%22%3EBest%20expandable%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20expandable%20hose%20from%20Flexi-Hose%20offers%20a%20creative%20solution%20for%20those%20who%20don't%20like%20dealing%20with%20long%20and%20unwieldy%20hoses.%20Its%20unique%20accordion-style%20body%20extends%20to%2050%20feet%20in%20length%20during%20use%20and%20quickly%20shrinks%20back%20down%20to%20a%20third%20of%20that%20length%20when%20the%20water%20is%20turned%20off.%20Unlike%20many%20traditional%20hard-sided%20hoses%2C%20this%20fabric-covered%20hose%20is%20soft%2C%20lightweight%2C%20and%20flexible.%20Thanks%20to%20its%20unique%20construction%20of%20a%20latex%20interior%20and%20polyester%20fabric%20exterior%2C%20it's%20also%20impossible%20to%20kink%20no%20matter%20how%20you%20twist%20or%20bend%20it.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20convenient%20brass%20valve%20lets%20you%20control%20the%20flow%20of%20water%20without%20a%20separate%20nozzle%20(although%20it%20also%20includes%20a%20multi-spray%20nozzle%20with%20eight%20settings).%20This%20lets%20you%20toggle%20between%20different%20water%20flow%20options%20or%20stop%20the%20flow%20completely%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20waste%20water%20as%20you%20carry%20your%20hose%20around.%20The%20way%20the%20hose%20expands%20and%20contracts%20in%20your%20hand%20when%20you%20switch%20flow%20options%20takes%20some%20getting%20used%20to%20and%20may%20cause%20a%20bit%20of%20discomfort%20at%20first.%20Be%20mindful%20not%20to%20drag%20the%20hose%20too%20far%20from%20the%20water%20connection%20when%20you%20use%20the%20valve%2C%20otherwise%20you'll%20be%20pulled%20back%20if%20the%20hose%20contracts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22TheFitLife%20Expandable%20Garden%20Hose%20coiled%20on%20a%20patch%20of%20green%20grass.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a8681a6d7e02001af88333%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EExpandable%20hoses%20like%20the%20Flexi-Hose%20is%20a%20good%20option%20if%20you%20occasionally%20need%20to%20reach%20farther%20away%2C%20but%20don't%20want%20do%20deal%20with%20long%20lengths%20of%20hose%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Rennie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20brass%20fittings%20are%20heavy-duty%20and%20durable.%20Unlike%20the%20plastic%20components%20on%20some%20other%20expandable%20hoses%2C%20they%20held%20up%20fine%20to%20our%20tossing%20them%20around%20on%20concrete.%20The%20fabric%20exterior%20isn't%20as%20rugged%20as%20traditional%20hoses%2C%20though%2C%20so%20you'll%20need%20to%20take%20extra%20care%20not%20to%20snag%20it%20on%20sharp%20or%20pointed%20objects%20or%20landscaping.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20this%20expandable%20hose%20is%20still%20a%20smart%20and%20effective%20way%20to%20complete%20all%20your%20watering%20tasks%20without%20compromising%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20heavy-duty%5C%22%3EBest%20heavy-duty%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20need%20complete%20and%20utter%20confidence%20that%20nothing%20will%20puncture%20or%20break%20your%20hose%2C%20get%20one%20made%20out%20of%20steel.%20The%20Tardigrade%20hose%20is%20heavy-duty%2C%20with%20none%20of%20the%20weight%20or%20thickness%20of%20a%20rubber%20hose.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20actively%20and%20aggressively%20tried%20to%20break%20it%20by%20dragging%20it%20across%20different%20terrains%20and%20jumping%20on%20it%2C%20but%20my%20efforts%20were%20futile.%20Rest%20assured%20that%20common%20concerns%20like%20pets%2C%20inclement%20weather%2C%20and%20thorny%2C%20rocky%20landscapes%20are%20no%20match.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20silver%20steel%20garden%20hose%20rolled%20up%20and%20lying%20on%20the%20grass%2C%20best%20heavy-duty%20garden%20hose%202022%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F603933bdd9208800185923c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Tardigrade%20Stainless%20Steel%20Hose%20is%20ultra-resistant%2C%20making%20it%20a%20good%20option%20for%20rugged%20terrain.%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20thinner%20and%20denser%20than%20a%20traditional%20rubber%20hose%2C%20but%20I%20found%20it%20relatively%20easy%20to%20maneuver%20around%20my%20backyard%20since%20it%20didn't%20twist%20and%20tangle.%20The%20steel%20body%20had%20a%20nice%20cool%20feeling%20as%20the%20water%20ran%20through%2C%20which%20also%20improved%20my%20watering%20experience.%20Its%20flow%20rate%2C%20while%20not%20as%20fast%20as%20those%20of%20the%20rubber%20options%20I%20tested%2C%20was%20decent%20at%207.5%20gallons%20per%20minute.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20pro%20to%20consider%3A%20The%20steel%20construction%20is%20UV-resistant%2C%20so%20you%20can%20leave%20the%20hose%20outside%2C%20and%20it%20won't%20get%20damaged%20by%20the%20sun%20and%20crack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20flexibility's%20sake%2C%20the%20body%20consists%20of%20many%20rings%20of%20stainless%20steel%2C%20which%20may%20pinch%20your%20fingers%20as%20you%20maneuver%20the%20hose.%20I%20recommend%20wearing%20gloves%20as%20a%20precaution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20drinking-water%20safe%5C%22%3EBest%20drinking-water%20safe%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20plan%20on%20drinking%20water%20out%20of%20your%20garden%20hose%2C%20the%20Water%20Right%20500%20Series%20Polyurethane%20Garden%20Hose%20is%20a%20great%20option.%20According%20to%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ecocenter.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fhealthy-stuff%2Fimages%2FGarden%2520Hose%2520Report%2520June%252020%25202016.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2016%20study%20by%20the%20Ecology%20Center%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20polyurethane%20and%20rubber%20were%20the%20only%20hose%20materials%20found%20not%20to%20have%20elevated%20levels%20of%20lead%2C%20bromine%2C%20or%20antimony%2C%20making%20this%20polyurethane%20model%20an%20easy%20choice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20extremely%20lightweight%20%E2%80%94%20just%205%20pounds%20for%2050%20feet%20of%20hose%20%E2%80%94%20which%20makes%20it%20comfortable%20to%20carry%20and%20store%20when%20not%20in%20use.%20Its%20sturdy%20construction%20provides%20a%20really%20solid%2C%20durable%20feel%2C%20and%20unlike%20some%20of%20the%20softer%2C%20more%20pliable%20hoses%20I%20tested%2C%20it%20barely%20lost%20any%20flow%20when%20stepped%20on.%20It%20also%20fared%20well%20in%20my%20abrasion%20tests%2C%20with%20only%20some%20minor%20cosmetic%20scuffs%20after%20tossing%20around%20a%20concrete%20walkway.%20The%20strain%20relief%20collars%20on%20either%20end%20are%20always%20nice%20to%20see%2C%20protecting%20the%20connection%20ends%20from%20harmful%20and%20frustrating%20kinks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Water%20Right%20500%20Series%20Polyurethane%20Garden%20Hose%20coiled%20on%20a%20patch%20of%20green%20grass.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a86b538ed31300199e26f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20shouldn't%20drink%20out%20of%20most%20garden%20hoses%3B%20this%20Water%20Right%20is%20an%20exception.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Rennie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKeep%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20Water%20Right%20500%20Series%20Polyurethane%20Garden%20Hose%20was%20a%20bit%20less%20flexible%20than%20some%20of%20the%20other%20hoses%20we%20tested%20and%20kept%20its%20coil%20memory%20tighter.%20That%20said%2C%20if%20your%20priority%20is%20safe%20and%20non-toxic%20drinking%20water%20for%20you%20and%20your%20family%2C%20we%20consider%20that%20a%20reasonable%20trade-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20extra-long%5C%22%3EBest%20extra-long%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%2025-%20or%2050-foot%20hose%20options%20are%20too%20short%20for%20your%20property%20or%20gardening%20project%2C%20consider%20the%20Flexzilla%20100-Foot%20Garden%20Hose.%20Flexibility%20is%20especially%20important%20when%20dealing%20with%20longer%20hoses%2C%20and%20the%20main%20reason%20we%20chose%20this%20ultra-flexible%20option%20as%20our%20top%20extra-long%20hose.%20Unlike%20more%20rigid%20hoses%20we've%20used%20and%20tested%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20Flexzilla%20is%20pliable%20enough%20to%20organize%20and%20loop%20together%2C%20maneuver%20and%20snake%20around%20landscaping%20obstacles%20or%20plants%2C%20lay%20flat%20without%20coiling%20up%20on%20its%20own%2C%20and%20connect%20to%20a%20sprinkler%20without%20flopping%20it%20over.%20It%20also%20has%20very%20little%20coil%20%26quot%3Bmemory%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20makes%20it%20really%20easy%20to%20coil%20back%20up%20in%20the%20shape%20or%20style%20you%20prefer%20without%20excessive%20kinking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20longer%20your%20garden%20hose%2C%20the%20more%20of%20an%20impact%20its%20weight%20has%20on%20overall%20usability.%20Since%20any%20extra%20weight%20quickly%20adds%20up%20when%20coiling%20for%20storage%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20transporting%20to%20and%20from%20your%20spigot%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20hose%20reel%20%E2%80%94%20the%2014-pound%20weight%20of%20the%20Flexzilla%20is%20another%20major%20benefit.%20This%20lightweight%20also%20requires%20less%20effort%20to%20drag%20behind%20you%20while%20watering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Water%20Right%20500%20Series%20Polyurethane%20Garden%20Hose%20coiled%20on%20a%20patch%20of%20green%20grass.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a869ba8ed31300199e2682%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20100-foot%20garden%20hose%20is%20very%20flexible%20and%20great%20for%20big%20lawns%2C%20but%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20it%20does%20pinch%20on%20obstacles%20and%20around%20corners.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Rennie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20found%20the%20hybrid%20polymer%20construction%20to%20be%20durable%20in%20regard%20to%20abrasions%20and%20scuffing.%20Even%20after%20tossing%20it%20around%20the%20concrete%20ground%20and%20%26quot%3Baccidentally%26quot%3B%20stepping%20on%20it%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20we%20failed%20to%20notice%20any%20measurable%20abrasions%20or%20other%20wear%20and%20tear.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20the%20overall%20flexibility%20of%20this%20material%20does%20result%20in%20a%20hose%20that's%20more%20likely%20to%20crimp%20and%20pinch%20around%20corners%2C%20unlike%20a%20heavier-duty%20hose%20with%20a%20harder%2C%20more%20rigid%20sheath%20around%20the%20exterior.%20Just%20make%20sure%20you're%20comfortable%20compromising%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20rigidity%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20lighter%2C%20easier%20to%20manipulate%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EType%20of%20hose%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESeveral%20types%20of%20garden%20hoses%20are%20available%2C%20so%20make%20sure%20to%20pick%20the%20best%20option%20for%C2%A0your%20garden's%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELight-duty%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThese%20hoses%20are%20ideal%20for%20smaller%20tasks%2C%20like%20watering%20the%20potted%20plants%20on%20your%20patio%2C%20or%20compact%20flower%20beds%20in%20your%20yard.%20They're%20relatively%20short%20and%20lightweight%2C%20and%20are%20convenient%20to%20coil%20up%20and%20store%20easily.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStandard%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWell-suited%20for%20general%2C%20all-around%20watering%20tasks%2C%20standard%20hoses%20are%20sturdy%20enough%20to%20handle%20the%20wear%20and%20tear%20of%20frequent%20use.%20They're%20heavier%20and%20typically%20longer%20than%20light-duty%20options%2C%20though%2C%20and%20may%20benefit%20from%20a%20hose%20hider%20or%20reel%20for%20storage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeavy-duty%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMade%20of%20thick%2C%20durable%20material%2C%20these%20hoses%20are%20rugged%20enough%20to%20be%20used%20effectively%20with%20pressure%20washers.%20This%20translates%20to%20a%20more%20expensive%20hose%20but%20also%20one%20with%20a%20much%20longer%20lifespan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EExpandable%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20lightweight%2C%20accordion-style%20design%20of%20these%20hoses%20allow%20them%20to%20contract%20when%20not%20in%20use%2C%20and%20easily%20expand%20when%20water%20flows%20through.%20This%20flexibility%20makes%20them%20very%20convenient%20to%20store%20and%20transport%2C%20although%20the%20fabric%20exterior%20is%20vulnerable%20to%20snags%20and%20rips.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoaker%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EInstead%20of%20spraying%20water%20out%20of%20a%20single%20outlet%2C%20soaker%20hoses%20release%20water%20through%20thousands%20of%20tiny%20pores.%20When%20laid%20on%20the%20ground%20throughout%20your%20garden%20bed%2C%20they%20provide%20a%20slow%2C%20efficient%20supply%20of%20water%20directly%20to%20the%20base%20of%20your%20plants.%20These%20hoses%20conserve%20water%20the%20best%20but%20are%20less%20functional%20than%20typical%20garden%20hoses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlat%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThese%20compact%20hoses%20are%20made%20of%20a%20flexible%20material%20that%20lays%20flat%20when%20empty%20and%20expands%20to%20full%20diameter%20when%20filled%20with%20water.%20They%20roll%20and%20coil%20up%20easily%2C%20although%20they're%20not%20as%20durable%20as%20rigid%20hoses.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Make%20sure%20your%20hose%20material%20is%20best%20suited%20for%20you%20and%20your%20watering%20needs.%20If%20your%20property%20is%20rough%20and%20rocky%20for%20example%2C%20choose%20a%20material%20that's%20durable%20enough%20to%20handle%20frequent%20wear%20and%20tear.%20If%20you%20plan%20on%20drinking%20out%20of%20your%20hose%2C%20go%20with%20a%20rubber%20or%20polyurethane%20option.%20You%20can%20find%20out%20more%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-garden-hose%23materials-10%5C%22%3Ebest%20hose%20materials%3C%2Fa%3E%20further%20down%20in%20this%20guide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERubber%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20tough%2C%20durable%20material%20is%20used%20in%20high-quality%2C%20heavy-duty%20hoses%20and%20is%20less%20likely%20to%20kink.%20It's%20expensive%20though%2C%20and%20heavier%20than%20most%20hose%20types.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EVinyl%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELess%20durable%20than%20rubber%2C%20vinyl%20hoses%20are%20the%20cheapest%20and%20best%20for%20light-duty%20watering%20jobs.%20If%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20compromise%20quality%20for%20affordability%2C%20look%20for%20a%20hose%20with%20both%20vinyl%20and%20rubber%20construction.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolyurethane%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20non-toxic%20material%20doesn't%20leach%20contaminants%2C%20making%20it%20safe%20for%20drinking%20out%20of.%20It's%20also%20strong%20and%20flexible%20enough%20to%20last%20a%20long%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EReinforced%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0A%20mesh%20lining%20between%20the%20layers%20of%20a%20hose%20adds%20extra%20durability%2C%20making%20them%20less%20prone%20to%20splitting%20and%20better-suited%20to%20high-pressure%20applications.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStainless%20steel%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHoses%20encased%20in%20flexible%20stainless%20steel%20coils%20provide%20maximum%20protection%20while%20still%20remaining%20flexible%20and%20easy%20to%20coil%20up.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDrinking-water%20safe%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E100%25%20rubber%20and%20polyurethane%20hoses%20are%20safe%20for%20drinking%20out%20of%2C%20since%20they%20are%20free%20of%20BPA%2C%20lead%2C%20and%20other%20harmful%20contaminants.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELength%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Hose%20length%20is%20important%20because%20if%20it's%20too%20long%2C%20you'll%20waste%20energy%20dragging%20around%20extra%20weight%20and%20valuable%20time%20coiling%20it%20back%20up.%20If%20it%20is%20too%20short%2C%20it%20won't%20be%20long%20enough%20to%20function%20properly.%20Consider%20the%20size%20of%20the%20area%20being%20watered%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20distance%20from%20the%20spigot%20to%20your%20sprinkler%2C%20car%2C%20or%20garden%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHose%20diameter%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20larger%20the%20diameter%20of%20your%20hose%2C%20the%20more%20water%20it%20can%20provide%2C%20but%20the%20heavier%20it%20gets.%20If%20maximum%20water%20output%20isn't%20a%20priority%2C%20consider%20going%20with%20a%20smaller%20diameter%20hose%20for%20convenience.%20Garden%20hoses%20typically%20range%20from%20%E2%85%9C%20to%20%E2%85%9D-inches%20in%20diameter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECoupling%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20These%20are%20the%20threaded%20components%20that%20connect%20the%20hose%20to%20the%20spigot%20on%20one%20end%20and%20the%20spray%20nozzle%20on%20the%20other.%20Metal%20couplings%20are%20preferred%2C%20with%20brass%20being%20the%20best%20option%20overall%20due%20to%20its%20durability.%20Plastic%20couplings%20are%20cheaper%20but%20are%20easily%20broken%20and%20are%20not%20practical%20for%20heavy-duty%20or%20frequent%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPSI%20(Pounds%20per%20square%20inch)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20determines%20the%20amount%20of%20pressure%20the%20hose%20can%20safely%20handle%20to%20avoid%20bursting%20or%20splitting.%20The%20best%20PSI%20for%20you%20ultimately%20depends%20on%20the%20pressure%20of%20the%20water%20coming%20out%20of%20your%20spigot%2C%20which%20can%20vary%2C%20but%20around%20350%20PSI%20is%20a%20good%20all-around%20number%20for%20general%20home%20use.%20If%20you%20plan%20on%20using%20your%20hose%20with%20a%20pressure%20washer%2C%20double%20check%20that%20its%20PSI%20is%20compatible%20with%20the%20PSI%20of%20the%20machine%20you're%20connecting%20it%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%20garden%20hoses%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20side%20images%20of%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20spraying%20water%20on%20a%20plant%20from%20a%20black%20garden%20hose%20on%20the%20left%20and%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20hand%20holding%20a%20light%20blue%20folded%20garden%20hose.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6039365605ddb100195f6729%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20picks%20for%20best%20garden%20hose%20are%20based%20on%20our%20hands-on%20testing.%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20put%20all%2013%20hoses%20through%20these%20same%20four%20tests%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20How%20easy%20was%20it%20to%20move%20the%20hose%20around%2C%20roll%20it%20up%2C%20and%20water%20plants%3F%20We%20rated%20the%20difficulty%20on%20a%20scale%20of%201-5%2C%20with%201%20being%20%26quot%3Bvery%20easy%2C%20barely%20broke%20a%20sweat%26quot%3B%20and%205%20being%20%26quot%3Bvery%20difficult%2C%20required%20significant%20effort.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20dragged%20each%20hose%2050%20feet%20across%20both%20concrete%20and%20grass%20and%20hit%20the%20fittings%20on%20the%20ground%20at%20different%20angles%2050%20times.%20Then%20we%20noted%20any%20abrasion%20and%20other%20durability%20issues%20with%20the%20hose%20body%20and%20the%20fitting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKink%20resistance%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20bent%20each%20hose%20in%20a%20tight%20%26quot%3BU%26quot%3B%20shape%20and%20stepped%20on%20each%20hose%20%E2%80%94%20repeating%20this%20sequence%20five%20times%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0to%20see%20how%20it%20snapped%20back%20or%20remained%20bent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlow%20rate%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20timed%20how%20long%20it%20took%20for%20the%20hose%20to%20fill%20a%20two-gallon%20bucket%20and%20recorded%20the%20flow%20rate%20in%20gallons%20per%20minute.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EGarden%20hose%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20coiled%20purple%20hose%20on%20driveway%20pavement%20with%20water%20leaking%20out.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F646e21d6a739dc0018092b05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBelow%20we%20answer%20frequently%20asked%20questions%20about%20buying%20and%20caring%20for%20a%20garden%20hose.%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20size%20hose%20should%20you%20buy%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20depends%20on%20the%20size%20of%20your%20lawn%20and%20proximity%20to%20your%20water%20connection.%20Coulter%20Lewis%2C%20founder%20of%20lawn%20care%20subscription%20startup%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.getsunday.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESunday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20you%20should%20consider%20at%20least%20a%2050-foot%20hose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20lawn%20is%20500-2%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20look%20for%20a%20hose%20that's%2050%20feet%20long.%20If%20your%20lawn%20is%202%2C000-5%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20look%20for%20a%20hose%20that's%20more%20than%2075%20feet.%20For%20more%20flexibility%2C%20consider%20buying%20two%20shorter%20hoses%20or%20an%20additional%20short%20extension%20hose%20to%20combine%20when%20needed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20advised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20guide%2C%20we%20focused%20on%2050-foot%20hoses.%20They%20are%20also%20available%20in%20shorter%20and%20longer%20lengths.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat's%20the%20best%20material%20for%20a%20garden%20hose%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20common%20constructions%20for%20the%20hose%20body%20are%20rubber%2C%20polyurethane%2C%20and%20vinyl.%20Jors%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRubber%20tends%20to%20be%20more%20flexible%2C%20but%20%5Bit's%5D%20also%20the%20heaviest.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20it's%20less%20susceptible%20to%20cuts%20and%20will%20stand%20up%20to%20rocky%20landscapes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20something%20that's%20lighter%2C%20more%20kink-resistant%2C%20and%20safe%20for%20drinking%20water%2C%20polyurethane%20and%20other%20hybrid%20composite%20materials%20are%20best.%20Vinyl%20is%20the%20cheapest%20but%20also%20the%20most%20prone%20to%20kinking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20fitting%20%E2%80%94%20the%20part%20that%20connects%20your%20hose%20to%20the%20water%20source%20or%20another%20hose%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0you%20should%20look%20for%20a%20metal%20construction.%20%26quot%3BFaceted%20brass%2C%20nickel-plated%2C%20or%20stainless%20steel%20is%20always%20recommended.%20Plastic%20couplings%2C%20although%20less%20expensive%2C%20do%20not%20stand%20up%20to%20heavy-duty%20use%20and%20tend%20to%20crack%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20you%20reduce%20and%20get%20rid%20of%20kinks%20in%20your%20hose%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20get%20a%20strong%20and%20flexible%20hose%20to%20reduce%20the%20chance%20of%20kinking.%20Beyond%20looking%20for%20rubber%20or%20polyurethane%2C%20you%20should%20also%20use%20a%20hose%20reel%20to%20wind%20the%20hose%20in%20a%20controlled%20fashion%2C%20recommends%20Jors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20you%20need%20a%20garden%20hose%20nozzle%20for%20your%20hose%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20highly%20recommend%20adding%20a%20nozzle%20to%20your%20hose.%20A%20nozzle%20lets%20you%20turn%20the%20flow%20of%20water%20on%20and%20off%2C%20saving%20you%20water.%20It%20also%20helps%20you%20distribute%20the%20right%20flow%20of%20water%20for%20your%20specific%20task%20(e.g.%2C%20power%20washing%20a%20deck%20vs.%20watering%20delicate%20flowers).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tested%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-garden-hose-nozzle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20garden%20hose%20nozzles%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat's%20the%20best%20way%20to%20store%20and%20extend%20the%20longevity%20of%20your%20hose%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProper%20storage%20of%20your%20garden%20hose%20will%20extend%20its%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jors.%20%26quot%3BI%20prefer%20a%20hose%20hanger%2C%20or%20in%20particular%20a%20hose%20reel.%20It's%20important%20when%20not%20in%20use%20to%20keep%20the%20hose%20off%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20a%20hose%20hanger%20or%20hose%20reel%20will%20accomplish%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20drain%20your%20hose%20after%20each%20use%20and%20before%20storage.%20Hot%20and%20frozen%20water%20can%20damage%20your%20hose.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20long%20should%20my%20garden%20hose%20last%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20depends%20on%20how%20well%20it's%20treated%20and%20the%20climate%20of%20your%20area%2C%20but%20a%20good-quality%20garden%20hose%20should%20last%20at%20least%20five%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20can%20I%20prevent%20kinking%20and%20knotting%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20way%20to%20prevent%20kinking%20and%20knotting%20is%20to%20coil%20your%20hose%20up%20as%20loosely%20as%20possible%2C%20or%2C%20even%20better%2C%20store%20it%20in%20a%20hose%20reel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20rolled%20rubber%20purple%20colorstorm%20garden%20hose%20lying%20on%20the%20grass%20%2C%20the%20best%20garden%20hose%20overall%202022%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60392fed05ddb100195f66e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDespite%20its%20heavy%20weight%2C%20the%20Dramm%20ColorStorm%20Garden%20Hose%20provides%20an%20efficient%20and%20surprisingly%20smooth%20watering%20experience.%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dramm%20ColorStorm%20Garden%20Hose%20was%20the%20clear%20winner%20in%20all%20of%20our%20tests.%20Although%20it%20was%20the%20heaviest%20of%20all%20the%20hoses%20we%20tried%2C%20it%20excelled%20in%20other%20areas%2C%20from%20ease%20of%20use%20to%20kink%20resistance%20to%20flow%20rate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20material%20and%20design%20make%20it%20a%20high-performing%2C%20reliable%20hose.%20Jors%20told%20us%20he%20personally%20prefers%20a%20high-quality%20rubber%20hose%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20properly%20stored%2C%20preferably%20on%20a%20reel%2C%20and%20drained%20after%20every%20use%2C%20it%20should%20last%20a%20very%20long%20time%20and%20make%20for%20happy%20gardening.%26quot%3B%20This%20hose%20is%20made%20from%20thick%20rubber%20and%20has%20angled%20rather%20than%20smooth%20sides%2C%20which%20prevent%20it%20from%20kinking%20and%20bending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rubber%20bounces%20back%20easily%20no%20matter%20how%20you%20twist%20it%2C%20bend%20it%2C%20or%20step%20on%20it%2C%20so%20all%20you%20really%20have%20to%20focus%20on%20while%20watering%20is%20dragging%20the%20hose%20in%20the%20right%20direction.%20After%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20being%20slammed%20against%20concrete%20and%20thrown%20about%2C%20the%20nickel-plated%20brass%20fittings%20held%20up%20well%2C%20with%20no%20warping%20or%20dents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20fit%20very%20securely%20and%20tightly%20on%20my%20water%20connection%2C%20and%20it%20had%20the%20fastest%20water%20flow%20of%20all%20the%20hose%20contenders%3A%2010.91%20gallons%20per%20minute.%20That%20makes%20it%20especially%20valuable%20for%20tasks%20like%20filling%20up%20a%20pool%20or%20large%20bucket.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20ground%20to%20water%2C%20the%20Dramm%20hose%20will%20make%20the%20chore%20go%20by%20quickly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20more%20expensive%20than%20the%20average%20hose%2C%20the%20investment%20is%20well%20worth%20it.%20Watering%20your%20garden%20or%20washing%20your%20car%20becomes%20significantly%20more%20pleasant%2C%20and%20you%20won't%20have%20to%20replace%20it%20because%20of%20hose%20body%20damage%20or%20frequent%20kinking.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20it%20comes%20in%20bright%20colors%20that%20make%20backyard%20chores%20a%20little%20more%20fun.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20budget%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%2050-ft%20rolled%20rubber%20black%20continental%20garden%20hose%20lying%20on%20the%20grass%2C%20best%20cheap%20hose%20of%202022%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60393145d9208800185923ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAt%20around%20%2450%2C%20the%20Continental%20Black%20Water%20Hose%20is%20a%20bit%20cheaper%20than%20other%20options%2C%20but%20still%20offers%20good%20durability.%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20find%20a%20cheap%20hose%20that%20doesn't%20compromise%20some%20features%2C%20be%20it%20durability%2C%20kink%20resistance%2C%20or%20weather%20resistance.%20For%20the%20most%20part%2C%20what%20you%20pay%20for%20is%20what%20you%20get%20in%20the%20hose%20department.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20one%20exception%3A%20the%20Continental%20hose.%20It's%20not%20dirt-cheap%2C%20but%20it%20is%20more%20affordable%20than%20all%20of%20our%20other%20picks%2C%20and%20it%20performs%20very%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hose%20is%20heavy%2C%20rugged%2C%20and%20durable.%20It%20has%20a%20thick%20rubber%20body%20and%20strong%20solid%20brass%20fittings%20that%20held%20up%20to%20repeated%20attacks%20against%20concrete.%20Overall%2C%20it%20provides%20a%20smooth%20and%20relatively%20easy%20watering%20experience%20because%20it%20fits%20tightly%20over%20the%20water%20connection%20and%20doesn't%20kink%20or%20bend.%20The%20most%20difficult%20part%20is%20dragging%20around%20the%2012%20pounds%20of%20weight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20flow%20rate%20is%20pretty%20good%20%E2%80%94%C2%A08.57%20gallons%20per%20minute%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0which%20is%20a%20little%20slower%20than%20our%20top%20pick%2C%20the%20Dramm%20hose.%20While%20I'd%20say%20the%20two%20hoses%20are%20pretty%20comparable%2C%20the%20Continental%20is%20slightly%20thicker%20and%20less%20efficient%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20come%20in%20multiple%20colors%20(just%20black).%20That%20being%20said%2C%20these%20flaws%20aren't%20insurmountable%2C%20and%20I%20was%20still%20satisfied%20with%20this%20budget%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20expandable%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22TheFitLife%20Expandable%20Garden%20Hose%20coiled%20on%20a%20patch%20of%20green%20grass.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a8681a6d7e02001af88333%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EExpandable%20hoses%20like%20the%20Flexi-Hose%20is%20a%20good%20option%20if%20you%20occasionally%20need%20to%20reach%20farther%20away%2C%20but%20don't%20want%20do%20deal%20with%20long%20lengths%20of%20hose%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Rennie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20expandable%20hose%20from%20Flexi-Hose%20offers%20a%20creative%20solution%20for%20those%20who%20don't%20like%20dealing%20with%20long%20and%20unwieldy%20hoses.%20Its%20unique%20accordion-style%20body%20extends%20to%2050%20feet%20in%20length%20during%20use%20and%20quickly%20shrinks%20back%20down%20to%20a%20third%20of%20that%20length%20when%20the%20water%20is%20turned%20off.%20Unlike%20many%20traditional%20hard-sided%20hoses%2C%20this%20fabric-covered%20hose%20is%20soft%2C%20lightweight%2C%20and%20flexible.%20Thanks%20to%20its%20unique%20construction%20of%20a%20latex%20interior%20and%20polyester%20fabric%20exterior%2C%20it's%20also%20impossible%20to%20kink%20no%20matter%20how%20you%20twist%20or%20bend%20it.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20convenient%20brass%20valve%20lets%20you%20control%20the%20flow%20of%20water%20without%20a%20separate%20nozzle%20(although%20it%20also%20includes%20a%20multi-spray%20nozzle%20with%20eight%20settings).%20This%20lets%20you%20toggle%20between%20different%20water%20flow%20options%20or%20stop%20the%20flow%20completely%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20waste%20water%20as%20you%20carry%20your%20hose%20around.%20The%20way%20the%20hose%20expands%20and%20contracts%20in%20your%20hand%20when%20you%20switch%20flow%20options%20takes%20some%20getting%20used%20to%20and%20may%20cause%20a%20bit%20of%20discomfort%20at%20first.%20Be%20mindful%20not%20to%20drag%20the%20hose%20too%20far%20from%20the%20water%20connection%20when%20you%20use%20the%20valve%2C%20otherwise%20you'll%20be%20pulled%20back%20if%20the%20hose%20contracts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20brass%20fittings%20are%20heavy-duty%20and%20durable.%20Unlike%20the%20plastic%20components%20on%20some%20other%20expandable%20hoses%2C%20they%20held%20up%20fine%20to%20our%20tossing%20them%20around%20on%20concrete.%20The%20fabric%20exterior%20isn't%20as%20rugged%20as%20traditional%20hoses%2C%20though%2C%20so%20you'll%20need%20to%20take%20extra%20care%20not%20to%20snag%20it%20on%20sharp%20or%20pointed%20objects%20or%20landscaping.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20this%20expandable%20hose%20is%20still%20a%20smart%20and%20effective%20way%20to%20complete%20all%20your%20watering%20tasks%20without%20compromising%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20heavy-duty%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20silver%20steel%20garden%20hose%20rolled%20up%20and%20lying%20on%20the%20grass%2C%20best%20heavy-duty%20garden%20hose%202022%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F603933bdd9208800185923c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Tardigrade%20Stainless%20Steel%20Hose%20is%20ultra-resistant%2C%20making%20it%20a%20good%20option%20for%20rugged%20terrain.%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20need%20complete%20and%20utter%20confidence%20that%20nothing%20will%20puncture%20or%20break%20your%20hose%2C%20get%20one%20made%20out%20of%20steel.%20The%20Tardigrade%20hose%20is%20heavy-duty%2C%20with%20none%20of%20the%20weight%20or%20thickness%20of%20a%20rubber%20hose.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20actively%20and%20aggressively%20tried%20to%20break%20it%20by%20dragging%20it%20across%20different%20terrains%20and%20jumping%20on%20it%2C%20but%20my%20efforts%20were%20futile.%20Rest%20assured%20that%20common%20concerns%20like%20pets%2C%20inclement%20weather%2C%20and%20thorny%2C%20rocky%20landscapes%20are%20no%20match.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20thinner%20and%20denser%20than%20a%20traditional%20rubber%20hose%2C%20but%20I%20found%20it%20relatively%20easy%20to%20maneuver%20around%20my%20backyard%20since%20it%20didn't%20twist%20and%20tangle.%20The%20steel%20body%20had%20a%20nice%20cool%20feeling%20as%20the%20water%20ran%20through%2C%20which%20also%20improved%20my%20watering%20experience.%20Its%20flow%20rate%2C%20while%20not%20as%20fast%20as%20those%20of%20the%20rubber%20options%20I%20tested%2C%20was%20decent%20at%207.5%20gallons%20per%20minute.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20pro%20to%20consider%3A%20The%20steel%20construction%20is%20UV-resistant%2C%20so%20you%20can%20leave%20the%20hose%20outside%2C%20and%20it%20won't%20get%20damaged%20by%20the%20sun%20and%20crack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20flexibility's%20sake%2C%20the%20body%20consists%20of%20many%20rings%20of%20stainless%20steel%2C%20which%20may%20pinch%20your%20fingers%20as%20you%20maneuver%20the%20hose.%20I%20recommend%20wearing%20gloves%20as%20a%20precaution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20drinking-water%20safe%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Water%20Right%20500%20Series%20Polyurethane%20Garden%20Hose%20coiled%20on%20a%20patch%20of%20green%20grass.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a86b538ed31300199e26f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20shouldn't%20drink%20out%20of%20most%20garden%20hoses%3B%20this%20Water%20Right%20is%20an%20exception.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Rennie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20plan%20on%20drinking%20water%20out%20of%20your%20garden%20hose%2C%20the%20Water%20Right%20500%20Series%20Polyurethane%20Garden%20Hose%20is%20a%20great%20option.%20According%20to%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ecocenter.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fhealthy-stuff%2Fimages%2FGarden%2520Hose%2520Report%2520June%252020%25202016.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2016%20study%20by%20the%20Ecology%20Center%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20polyurethane%20and%20rubber%20were%20the%20only%20hose%20materials%20found%20not%20to%20have%20elevated%20levels%20of%20lead%2C%20bromine%2C%20or%20antimony%2C%20making%20this%20polyurethane%20model%20an%20easy%20choice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20extremely%20lightweight%20%E2%80%94%20just%205%20pounds%20for%2050%20feet%20of%20hose%20%E2%80%94%20which%20makes%20it%20comfortable%20to%20carry%20and%20store%20when%20not%20in%20use.%20Its%20sturdy%20construction%20provides%20a%20really%20solid%2C%20durable%20feel%2C%20and%20unlike%20some%20of%20the%20softer%2C%20more%20pliable%20hoses%20I%20tested%2C%20it%20barely%20lost%20any%20flow%20when%20stepped%20on.%20It%20also%20fared%20well%20in%20my%20abrasion%20tests%2C%20with%20only%20some%20minor%20cosmetic%20scuffs%20after%20tossing%20around%20a%20concrete%20walkway.%20The%20strain%20relief%20collars%20on%20either%20end%20are%20always%20nice%20to%20see%2C%20protecting%20the%20connection%20ends%20from%20harmful%20and%20frustrating%20kinks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeep%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20Water%20Right%20500%20Series%20Polyurethane%20Garden%20Hose%20was%20a%20bit%20less%20flexible%20than%20some%20of%20the%20other%20hoses%20we%20tested%20and%20kept%20its%20coil%20memory%20tighter.%20That%20said%2C%20if%20your%20priority%20is%20safe%20and%20non-toxic%20drinking%20water%20for%20you%20and%20your%20family%2C%20we%20consider%20that%20a%20reasonable%20trade-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20extra-long%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Water%20Right%20500%20Series%20Polyurethane%20Garden%20Hose%20coiled%20on%20a%20patch%20of%20green%20grass.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a869ba8ed31300199e2682%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20100-foot%20garden%20hose%20is%20very%20flexible%20and%20great%20for%20big%20lawns%2C%20but%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20it%20does%20pinch%20on%20obstacles%20and%20around%20corners.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Rennie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%2025-%20or%2050-foot%20hose%20options%20are%20too%20short%20for%20your%20property%20or%20gardening%20project%2C%20consider%20the%20Flexzilla%20100-Foot%20Garden%20Hose.%20Flexibility%20is%20especially%20important%20when%20dealing%20with%20longer%20hoses%2C%20and%20the%20main%20reason%20we%20chose%20this%20ultra-flexible%20option%20as%20our%20top%20extra-long%20hose.%20Unlike%20more%20rigid%20hoses%20we've%20used%20and%20tested%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20Flexzilla%20is%20pliable%20enough%20to%20organize%20and%20loop%20together%2C%20maneuver%20and%20snake%20around%20landscaping%20obstacles%20or%20plants%2C%20lay%20flat%20without%20coiling%20up%20on%20its%20own%2C%20and%20connect%20to%20a%20sprinkler%20without%20flopping%20it%20over.%20It%20also%20has%20very%20little%20coil%20%26quot%3Bmemory%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20makes%20it%20really%20easy%20to%20coil%20back%20up%20in%20the%20shape%20or%20style%20you%20prefer%20without%20excessive%20kinking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20longer%20your%20garden%20hose%2C%20the%20more%20of%20an%20impact%20its%20weight%20has%20on%20overall%20usability.%20Since%20any%20extra%20weight%20quickly%20adds%20up%20when%20coiling%20for%20storage%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20transporting%20to%20and%20from%20your%20spigot%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20hose%20reel%20%E2%80%94%20the%2014-pound%20weight%20of%20the%20Flexzilla%20is%20another%20major%20benefit.%20This%20lightweight%20also%20requires%20less%20effort%20to%20drag%20behind%20you%20while%20watering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20found%20the%20hybrid%20polymer%20construction%20to%20be%20durable%20in%20regard%20to%20abrasions%20and%20scuffing.%20Even%20after%20tossing%20it%20around%20the%20concrete%20ground%20and%20%26quot%3Baccidentally%26quot%3B%20stepping%20on%20it%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20we%20failed%20to%20notice%20any%20measurable%20abrasions%20or%20other%20wear%20and%20tear.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20the%20overall%20flexibility%20of%20this%20material%20does%20result%20in%20a%20hose%20that's%20more%20likely%20to%20crimp%20and%20pinch%20around%20corners%2C%20unlike%20a%20heavier-duty%20hose%20with%20a%20harder%2C%20more%20rigid%20sheath%20around%20the%20exterior.%20Just%20make%20sure%20you're%20comfortable%20compromising%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20rigidity%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20lighter%2C%20easier%20to%20manipulate%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20garden%20hose%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EType%20of%20hose%3A%20Several%20types%20of%20garden%20hoses%20are%20available%2C%20so%20make%20sure%20to%20pick%20the%20best%20option%20for%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0your%20garden's%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELight-duty%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThese%20hoses%20are%20ideal%20for%20smaller%20tasks%2C%20like%20watering%20the%20potted%20plants%20on%20your%20patio%2C%20or%20compact%20flower%20beds%20in%20your%20yard.%20They're%20relatively%20short%20and%20lightweight%2C%20and%20are%20convenient%20to%20coil%20up%20and%20store%20easily.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStandard%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWell-suited%20for%20general%2C%20all-around%20watering%20tasks%2C%20standard%20hoses%20are%20sturdy%20enough%20to%20handle%20the%20wear%20and%20tear%20of%20frequent%20use.%20They're%20heavier%20and%20typically%20longer%20than%20light-duty%20options%2C%20though%2C%20and%20may%20benefit%20from%20a%20hose%20hider%20or%20reel%20for%20storage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeavy-duty%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMade%20of%20thick%2C%20durable%20material%2C%20these%20hoses%20are%20rugged%20enough%20to%20be%20used%20effectively%20with%20pressure%20washers.%20This%20translates%20to%20a%20more%20expensive%20hose%20but%20also%20one%20with%20a%20much%20longer%20lifespan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EExpandable%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20lightweight%2C%20accordion-style%20design%20of%20these%20hoses%20allow%20them%20to%20contract%20when%20not%20in%20use%2C%20and%20easily%20expand%20when%20water%20flows%20through.%20This%20flexibility%20makes%20them%20very%20convenient%20to%20store%20and%20transport%2C%20although%20the%20fabric%20exterior%20is%20vulnerable%20to%20snags%20and%20rips.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoaker%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EInstead%20of%20spraying%20water%20out%20of%20a%20single%20outlet%2C%20soaker%20hoses%20release%20water%20through%20thousands%20of%20tiny%20pores.%20When%20laid%20on%20the%20ground%20throughout%20your%20garden%20bed%2C%20they%20provide%20a%20slow%2C%20efficient%20supply%20of%20water%20directly%20to%20the%20base%20of%20your%20plants.%20These%20hoses%20conserve%20water%20the%20best%20but%20are%20less%20functional%20than%20typical%20garden%20hoses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlat%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThese%20compact%20hoses%20are%20made%20of%20a%20flexible%20material%20that%20lays%20flat%20when%20empty%20and%20expands%20to%20full%20diameter%20when%20filled%20with%20water.%20They%20roll%20and%20coil%20up%20easily%2C%20although%20they're%20not%20as%20durable%20as%20rigid%20hoses.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Make%20sure%20your%20hose%20material%20is%20best%20suited%20for%20you%20and%20your%20watering%20needs.%20If%20your%20property%20is%20rough%20and%20rocky%20for%20example%2C%20choose%20a%20material%20that's%20durable%20enough%20to%20handle%20frequent%20wear%20and%20tear.%20If%20you%20plan%20on%20drinking%20out%20of%20your%20hose%2C%20go%20with%20a%20rubber%20or%20polyurethane%20option.%20You%20can%20find%20out%20more%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-garden-hose%23materials-10%5C%22%3Ebest%20hose%20materials%3C%2Fa%3E%20further%20down%20in%20this%20guide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERubber%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20tough%2C%20durable%20material%20is%20used%20in%20high-quality%2C%20heavy-duty%20hoses%20and%20is%20less%20likely%20to%20kink.%20It's%20expensive%20though%2C%20and%20heavier%20than%20most%20hose%20types.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EVinyl%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELess%20durable%20than%20rubber%2C%20vinyl%20hoses%20are%20the%20cheapest%20and%20best%20for%20light-duty%20watering%20jobs.%20If%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20compromise%20quality%20for%20affordability%2C%20look%20for%20a%20hose%20with%20both%20vinyl%20and%20rubber%20construction.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolyurethane%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20non-toxic%20material%20doesn't%20leach%20contaminants%2C%20making%20it%20safe%20for%20drinking%20out%20of.%20It's%20also%20strong%20and%20flexible%20enough%20to%20last%20a%20long%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EReinforced%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0A%20mesh%20lining%20between%20the%20layers%20of%20a%20hose%20adds%20extra%20durability%2C%20making%20them%20less%20prone%20to%20splitting%20and%20better-suited%20to%20high-pressure%20applications.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStainless%20steel%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHoses%20encased%20in%20flexible%20stainless%20steel%20coils%20provide%20maximum%20protection%20while%20still%20remaining%20flexible%20and%20easy%20to%20coil%20up.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDrinking-water%20safe%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E100%25%20rubber%20and%20polyurethane%20hoses%20are%20safe%20for%20drinking%20out%20of%2C%20since%20they%20are%20free%20of%20BPA%2C%20lead%2C%20and%20other%20harmful%20contaminants.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELength%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Hose%20length%20is%20important%20because%20if%20it's%20too%20long%2C%20you'll%20waste%20energy%20dragging%20around%20extra%20weight%20and%20valuable%20time%20coiling%20it%20back%20up.%20If%20it%20is%20too%20short%2C%20it%20won't%20be%20long%20enough%20to%20function%20properly.%20Consider%20the%20size%20of%20the%20area%20being%20watered%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20distance%20from%20the%20spigot%20to%20your%20sprinkler%2C%20car%2C%20or%20garden%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHose%20diameter%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20larger%20the%20diameter%20of%20your%20hose%2C%20the%20more%20water%20it%20can%20provide%2C%20but%20the%20heavier%20it%20gets.%20If%20maximum%20water%20output%20isn't%20a%20priority%2C%20consider%20going%20with%20a%20smaller%20diameter%20hose%20for%20convenience.%20Garden%20hoses%20typically%20range%20from%20%E2%85%9C%20to%20%E2%85%9D-inches%20in%20diameter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECoupling%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20These%20are%20the%20threaded%20components%20that%20connect%20the%20hose%20to%20the%20spigot%20on%20one%20end%20and%20the%20spray%20nozzle%20on%20the%20other.%20Metal%20couplings%20are%20preferred%2C%20with%20brass%20being%20the%20best%20option%20overall%20due%20to%20its%20durability.%20Plastic%20couplings%20are%20cheaper%20but%20are%20easily%20broken%20and%20are%20not%20practical%20for%20heavy-duty%20or%20frequent%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPSI%20(Pounds%20per%20square%20inch)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20determines%20the%20amount%20of%20pressure%20the%20hose%20can%20safely%20handle%20to%20avoid%20bursting%20or%20splitting.%20The%20best%20PSI%20for%20you%20ultimately%20depends%20on%20the%20pressure%20of%20the%20water%20coming%20out%20of%20your%20spigot%2C%20which%20can%20vary%2C%20but%20around%20350%20PSI%20is%20a%20good%20all-around%20number%20for%20general%20home%20use.%20If%20you%20plan%20on%20using%20your%20hose%20with%20a%20pressure%20washer%2C%20double%20check%20that%20its%20PSI%20is%20compatible%20with%20the%20PSI%20of%20the%20machine%20you're%20connecting%20it%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20test%20garden%20hoses%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20side%20images%20of%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20spraying%20water%20on%20a%20plant%20from%20a%20black%20garden%20hose%20on%20the%20left%20and%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20hand%20holding%20a%20light%20blue%20folded%20garden%20hose.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6039365605ddb100195f6729%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20picks%20for%20best%20garden%20hose%20are%20based%20on%20our%20hands-on%20testing.%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20put%20all%2013%20hoses%20through%20these%20same%20four%20tests%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20How%20easy%20was%20it%20to%20move%20the%20hose%20around%2C%20roll%20it%20up%2C%20and%20water%20plants%3F%20We%20rated%20the%20difficulty%20on%20a%20scale%20of%201-5%2C%20with%201%20being%20%26quot%3Bvery%20easy%2C%20barely%20broke%20a%20sweat%26quot%3B%20and%205%20being%20%26quot%3Bvery%20difficult%2C%20required%20significant%20effort.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20dragged%20each%20hose%2050%20feet%20across%20both%20concrete%20and%20grass%20and%20hit%20the%20fittings%20on%20the%20ground%20at%20different%20angles%2050%20times.%20Then%20we%20noted%20any%20abrasion%20and%20other%20durability%20issues%20with%20the%20hose%20body%20and%20the%20fitting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKink%20resistance%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20bent%20each%20hose%20in%20a%20tight%20%26quot%3BU%26quot%3B%20shape%20and%20stepped%20on%20each%20hose%20%E2%80%94%20repeating%20this%20sequence%20five%20times%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0to%20see%20how%20it%20snapped%20back%20or%20remained%20bent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlow%20rate%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20timed%20how%20long%20it%20took%20for%20the%20hose%20to%20fill%20a%20two-gallon%20bucket%20and%20recorded%20the%20flow%20rate%20in%20gallons%20per%20minute.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGarden%20hose%20FAQs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20coiled%20purple%20hose%20on%20driveway%20pavement%20with%20water%20leaking%20out.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F646e21d6a739dc0018092b05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBelow%20we%20answer%20frequently%20asked%20questions%20about%20buying%20and%20caring%20for%20a%20garden%20hose.%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20size%20hose%20should%20you%20buy%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20depends%20on%20the%20size%20of%20your%20lawn%20and%20proximity%20to%20your%20water%20connection.%20Coulter%20Lewis%2C%20founder%20of%20lawn%20care%20subscription%20startup%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.getsunday.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESunday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20you%20should%20consider%20at%20least%20a%2050-foot%20hose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20lawn%20is%20500-2%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20look%20for%20a%20hose%20that's%2050%20feet%20long.%20If%20your%20lawn%20is%202%2C000-5%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20look%20for%20a%20hose%20that's%20more%20than%2075%20feet.%20For%20more%20flexibility%2C%20consider%20buying%20two%20shorter%20hoses%20or%20an%20additional%20short%20extension%20hose%20to%20combine%20when%20needed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20advised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20guide%2C%20we%20focused%20on%2050-foot%20hoses.%20They%20are%20also%20available%20in%20shorter%20and%20longer%20lengths.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat's%20the%20best%20material%20for%20a%20garden%20hose%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20common%20constructions%20for%20the%20hose%20body%20are%20rubber%2C%20polyurethane%2C%20and%20vinyl.%20Jors%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRubber%20tends%20to%20be%20more%20flexible%2C%20but%20%5Bit's%5D%20also%20the%20heaviest.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20it's%20less%20susceptible%20to%20cuts%20and%20will%20stand%20up%20to%20rocky%20landscapes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20something%20that's%20lighter%2C%20more%20kink-resistant%2C%20and%20safe%20for%20drinking%20water%2C%20polyurethane%20and%20other%20hybrid%20composite%20materials%20are%20best.%20Vinyl%20is%20the%20cheapest%20but%20also%20the%20most%20prone%20to%20kinking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20fitting%20%E2%80%94%20the%20part%20that%20connects%20your%20hose%20to%20the%20water%20source%20or%20another%20hose%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0you%20should%20look%20for%20a%20metal%20construction.%20%26quot%3BFaceted%20brass%2C%20nickel-plated%2C%20or%20stainless%20steel%20is%20always%20recommended.%20Plastic%20couplings%2C%20although%20less%20expensive%2C%20do%20not%20stand%20up%20to%20heavy-duty%20use%20and%20tend%20to%20crack%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20you%20reduce%20and%20get%20rid%20of%20kinks%20in%20your%20hose%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20get%20a%20strong%20and%20flexible%20hose%20to%20reduce%20the%20chance%20of%20kinking.%20Beyond%20looking%20for%20rubber%20or%20polyurethane%2C%20you%20should%20also%20use%20a%20hose%20reel%20to%20wind%20the%20hose%20in%20a%20controlled%20fashion%2C%20recommends%20Jors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20you%20need%20a%20garden%20hose%20nozzle%20for%20your%20hose%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20highly%20recommend%20adding%20a%20nozzle%20to%20your%20hose.%20A%20nozzle%20lets%20you%20turn%20the%20flow%20of%20water%20on%20and%20off%2C%20saving%20you%20water.%20It%20also%20helps%20you%20distribute%20the%20right%20flow%20of%20water%20for%20your%20specific%20task%20(e.g.%2C%20power%20washing%20a%20deck%20vs.%20watering%20delicate%20flowers).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tested%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-garden-hose-nozzle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20garden%20hose%20nozzles%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat's%20the%20best%20way%20to%20store%20and%20extend%20the%20longevity%20of%20your%20hose%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProper%20storage%20of%20your%20garden%20hose%20will%20extend%20its%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jors.%20%26quot%3BI%20prefer%20a%20hose%20hanger%2C%20or%20in%20particular%20a%20hose%20reel.%20It's%20important%20when%20not%20in%20use%20to%20keep%20the%20hose%20off%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20a%20hose%20hanger%20or%20hose%20reel%20will%20accomplish%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20drain%20your%20hose%20after%20each%20use%20and%20before%20storage.%20Hot%20and%20frozen%20water%20can%20damage%20your%20hose.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20long%20should%20my%20garden%20hose%20last%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20depends%20on%20how%20well%20it's%20treated%20and%20the%20climate%20of%20your%20area%2C%20but%20a%20good-quality%20garden%20hose%20should%20last%20at%20least%20five%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20can%20I%20prevent%20kinking%20and%20knotting%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20way%20to%20prevent%20kinking%20and%20knotting%20is%20to%20coil%20your%20hose%20up%20as%20loosely%20as%20possible%2C%20or%2C%20even%20better%2C%20store%20it%20in%20a%20hose%20reel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-garden-hose%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717709816000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F603934b105ddb100195f670f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-garden-hose%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20reliable%20water%20ho