ulars.%20But%20Groff%20supported%20her%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20her%20to%20figure%20things%20out%20on%20her%20own%2C%20but%20know%20that%20I'm%20there%20for%20whatever%20she%20needs%20me%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Groff%2C%20a%20state%20science%20fair%20director%20in%20Iowa%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e8eb9918-1eb6-4a44-b891-57a34acde1ed%5C%22%3ESend%20them%20to%20public%20school%20and%20travel%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20students%20at%20ISEF%20pursued%20solutions%20to%20problems%20in%20their%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Oahu%20resident%20Maddux%20Alexander%20Springer%2C%20one%20of%20the%20top%20winners%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteen-wins-top-award-sea-turtles-mysterious-tumors-investigation-hawaii-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestigated%20tumors%20that%20were%20killing%20sea%20turtles%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20his%20shores.%20And%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEstrada's%20daughter%2C%20Pauline%2C%20studied%20the%20herbicide-resistant%20weeds%20plaguing%20the%20farms%20surrounding%20her%20Fresno%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22girl%20in%20white%20jacket%20holding%20camera%20standing%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20table%20full%20of%20plant%20seedlings%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665fa2c4cc442a2f676e0520%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPauline%20Victoria%20Estrada%20with%20the%20plants%20she%20studied%20for%20her%20science%20fair%20project.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Estrada%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEstrada%20partially%20attributes%20her%20kids'%20community%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eengagement%20to%20their%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epublic%20school%2C%20where%20they%20grew%20up%20with%20people%20from%20different%20backgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20will%20learn%20a%20lot%20from%20being%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20sa