charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F636a840de53c920019e7eee7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESince%20making%20pizza%20requires%20such%20high%20temperatures%2C%20preheating%20the%20Ooni%20Koda%20is%20essential%20to%20successful%20pies.%3Cp%3EMolly%20Allen%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELetting%20the%20oven%20come%20to%20the%20proper%20temperature%20is%20crucial.%20The%20Koda%2016%20can%20reach%20a%20temperature%20of%20950%20degrees%20Fahrenheit.%20The%20oven%20needs%20to%20preheat%20for%20about%2020%20minutes%20to%20get%20to%20752%20degrees%2C%20the%20optimal%20pizza%20cooking%20temperature%20noted%20in%20the%20Ooni%20user%20guide.%20Using%20the%20infrared%20thermometer%20to%20check%20the%20temperature%20of%20the%20stone%20helps%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20oven%20is%20hot%20enough%20for%20cooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20it%20reaches%20that%20temperature%2C%20the%20oven%20cooks%20pizzas%20in%20less%20than%20a%20minute.%C2%A0Because%20the%20oven%20is%20so%20hot%2C%20the%20yeast%20in%20the%20dough%20puffs%20up%20and%20creates%20pockets%20of%20air.%20With%20a%20touch%20of%20char%20from%20the%20flames%2C%20you%20get%20the%20perfect%20balance%20of%20soft-meets-crispy%20crust.%20The%20key%20to%20the%20best%20bake%20is%20to%20turn%20the%20pizza%20every%2020%20seconds.%20This%20ensures%20an%20even%20cook%20and%20that%20one%20section%20of%20the%20pizza%20isn't%20getting%20more%20char%20than%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20active%20flame%20melts%20the%20cheese%20quickly%2C%20making%20it%20golden%20and%20bubbly%2C%20and%20toppings%20such%20as%20pepperoni%20or%20red%20peppers%20are%20singed%20by%20the%20flame%20for%20a%20touch%20of%20crispness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Capacity%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECapacity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pizza%20peel%20taking%20out%20a%20baked%20pizza%20with%20apples%20and%20pesto%20as%20toppings%2C%20from%20the%20Ooni%20Koda%2016%20Pizza%20Oven.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F636a8445e53c920019e7eefa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20make%20mini%20pizzas%20or%2016-inch%20pies%20in%20the%20Koda.%3Cp%3EMolly%20Allen%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Koda%2016%20can%20fit%20large%20and%20small%20pizzas%2C%20but%20I%20always%20make%20just%20one%20at%20a%20time.%20This%20is%20the%20larger%20oven%20of%20the%20Koda%20line%2C%20so%20you%20can%20easily%20cook%2016-inch%20pizzas%20in%20it.%20However%2C%20I%20always%20choose%20to%20go%20smaller.%20I%20prefer%20to%20make%20a%20number%20of%20different%20pizzas%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20toppings%2C%20especially%20if%20I%20have%20guests%20over%20for%20a%20pizza%20party.%20I%20get%20the%20best%20results%20when%20I%20cook%20each%20of%20the%20smaller%20pizzas%20separately.%20The%20cook%20time%20is%20so%20fast%20that%20focusing%20on%20turning%20just%20one%20pizza%20is%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20make%20other%20foods%20and%20even%20desserts%20in%20it%20too.%20You%20can%20use%20the%20oven%20at%20a%20lower%20temperature%20to%20make%20a%20variety%20of%20other%20dishes.%20Ooni%20sells%20cookware%20pieces%20such%20as%20cast%20iron%20skillets%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20cook%20steaks%2C%20chicken%2C%20and%20roast%20vegetables.%20I've%20successfully%20baked%20a%20fruit%20crisp%20in%20the%20oven%20as%20a%20great%2C%20quick%20dessert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ooni%20pizza%20oven%20is%20an%20expensive%20appliance%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20quite%20ready%20to%20use%20out%20of%20the%20box.%20You'll%20need%20to%20purchase%20other%20important%20tools%20separately%20to%20start%20making%20pizza.%20However%2C%20if%20you're%20a%20pizza%20lover%2C%20it%20is%20well%20worth%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20learning%20curve%20to%20master%20the%20oven%2C%20but%20with%20how%20fun%20it%20is%20to%20use%2C%20even%20the%20practice%20pizzas%20along%20the%20way%20are%20delicious.%20Plus%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20possibilities%20for%20using%20it%20to%20make%20other%20food%20and%20desserts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fooni-koda-16-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717701656000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F636a81a1e53c920019e7ee17%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fooni-koda-16-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Ooni%20Koda%2016%20pizza%20oven%20is%20an%20investment%2C%20but%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20make%20artisanal%20pizza%20pies%20at%20home.%20Here's%20how%20it%20works.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Molly%20Allen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fooni-koda-16-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98True%20Detective%3A%20Night%20Country%E2%80%99%20Stars%20Talk%20Inspiration%20and%20Connecting%20to%20Characters%20at%20Variety%E2%80%99s%20Indigenous%20Storytelling%20in%20Entertainment%20Breakfast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717701642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2F2156233880-e1717699409500.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236027514%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22HBO%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CTrue%20Detective%E2%80%9D%20took%20over%20television%20in%202014%20with%20Woody%20Harrelson%20and%20Mathew%20Mat