20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pellet-smoker%5C%22%3Ebest%20pellet%20smokers%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20oven%20gets%20up%20to%20temperature%20in%20as%20little%20as%2015%20minutes%20and%20a%2020-pound%20bag%20of%20wood%20pellets%20was%20enough%20to%20make%20about%2050%20pizzas.%20You%20have%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20pellets%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20airflow%20is%20just%20right%20and%20that%20they%20don't%20jam%20up%20in%20the%20metal%20tube.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flames%20are%20directed%20to%20the%20roof%20of%20the%20oven%20rather%20than%20directly%20onto%20the%20pizza%2C%20so%20you%20get%20excellent%20radiant%20heat.%20For%20best%20results%2C%20you%20should%20rotate%20the%20pizza%20every%2020%20to%2030%20seconds%20and%20keep%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20the%20pellets%20to%20ensure%20they%20are%20burning%20properly.%20We've%20also%20tested%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fooni-koda-16-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOoni%20Koda%2016%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20loved%20the%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20indoor%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20you%20bring%20the%20fiery%20furnace%20of%20a%20pizza%20oven%20indoors%3F%20One%20way%20is%20to%20get%20the%20Breville%20Smart%20Oven%20Pizzaiolo%20for%20your%20kitchen.%20This%20countertop%20appliance%20can%20reach%20temperatures%20of%20up%20to%20750%20degrees%20F%2C%20and%20is%20designed%20to%20emulate%20a%20brick%20oven%3B%20it's%20sealed%20to%20protect%20against%20heat%20loss%2C%20including%20the%20double-pane%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20Breville's%20Element%20IQ%20technology%2C%20the%20Pizzaiolo%20cooks%20pizza%20evenly%2C%20whether%20it's%20frozen%20or%20fresh.%20It%20also%20has%20settings%20for%20pizza%20styles%2C%20like%20thin-and-crispy%2C%20New%20York%2C%20or%20wood-fired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbreville-smart-oven-pizzaiolo-review-2018-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20our%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20found%20the%20oven%20only%20required%20a%20few%20minutes%20to%20preheat%2C%20which%20makes%20getting%20a%20pizza%20from%20dough%20to%20mouth%20even%20faster.%20Despite%20the%20small%20opening%2C%20the%20Pizzaiolo%20can%20cook%20other%20foods%20too%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20auto-eject%20door%20that%20facilitates%20easy%20removal%20of%20food%20from%20the%20oven.%20In%20our%20tests%2C%20pizzas%20baked%20evenly%20with%20just%20one%20spin%20(although%20this%20isn't%20really%20necessary).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20an%20expensive%20appliance%20that's%20really%20for%20a%20single%20purpose.%20If%20you%20love%20Neapolitan-style%20pizza%2C%20there's%20no%20other%20compact%20appliance%20that%20can%20achieve%20what%20the%20Pizzaiolo%20can.%20But%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20care%20about%20this%20particular%20style%20of%20pizza%2C%20you%20may%20be%20better%20served%20by%20Breville's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_080119_best-pizza-ovens-20%26h%3D70208bd773c46e6d5645f0715d04b8447779ac74743c6e74dcf2d8ac644375b2%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f426c2%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbest-pizza-ovens%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwilliams-sonoma.pdy5.net%252Fc%252F196318%252F265127%252F4291%253FsubId1%253Dbiipgf_080119_best-pizza-ovens%2526u%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.williams-sonoma.com%25252Fproducts%25252Fbreville-crispy-crust-pizza-maker%25252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECrispy%20Crust%20Pizza%20Maker%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20be%20had%20for%20around%20%24150%20and%20does%20a%20good%20enough%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20budget%3Cp%3EThough%20not%20shaped%20like%20a%20classic%20oven%2C%20the%20Pizzazz%20features%20a%2012-inch%20nonstick%20baking%20pan%20that%20rotates%20between%20two%20heating%20ele