sed%20compensation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20she%20doesn't%20expect%20Musk%20to%20sue%20Tesla%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20possibility.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vote%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk's%3C%2Fa%3E%20hotly%20debated%20%2455%20billion%20pay%20package%20is%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20compensation%20plan%2C%20originally%20put%20into%20place%20in%202018%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-strikes-down-elon-musk-tesla-compensation-pay-package-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estruck%20down%20earlier%20this%20year%20by%20a%20Delaware%20judge%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20said%20the%20billionaire%20had%20undue%20influence%20over%20the%20board%20because%20of%20close%20ties%20to%20some%20of%20its%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20is%20now%20putting%20Musk's%20pay%20package%20to%20a%20shareholder%20vote%20on%20June%2013%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20reinstate%20it.%20So%20what%20will%20happen%20if%20it%20isn't%20approved%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-chair-robyn-denholm-lets-elon-musk-take-the-spotlight-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%20board%20chair%20Robyn%20Denholm%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20CNBC's%20%26quot%3BSquawk%20Box%26quot%3B%20on%20Thursday%20that%20there%20are%20multiple%20possibilities.%20The%20board%20has%20considered%20options%20such%20as%20creating%20a%20new%20pay%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20but%20she%20said%20that%20could%20end%20up%20costing%20shareholders%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDenholm%20argued%20that%20the%20compensation%20tied%20to%20the%202018%20pay%20package%2C%20which%20was%20worth%20an%20estimated%20%242.3%20billion%20in%20stock-based%20compensation%20charges%20at%20the%20time%2C%20had%20already%20been%20paid%20out.%20Rejecting%20the%20plan%20wouldn't%20change%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20the%20shareholders%20overturn%20the%202018%20pay%20plan%2C%20and%20Tesla%20were%20to%20craft%20a%20new%20plan%20with%20the%20same%20stock%20grants%2C%20they%20would%20cost%20around%20%2425%20billion%20worth%20of%20stock-based%20compensation%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20whether%20Elon%20Musk%20could%20ultimately%20sue%20Tesla%20if%20shareholders%20reject%20ratification%2C%20Denholm%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bpossible%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20she%20didn't%20know%20how%20probable%20it%20would%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20the%20good%20part%20about%20the%20legal%20system%20in%20the%20US%20is%20anybody%20can%20sue%20anybody%2C%26quot%3B%20Denholm%20said.%20But%20Denholm%20said%20at%20this%20point%2C%20it%20wasn't%20something%20that%20Musk%20had%20brought%20up%20to%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tesla%20board%20chair%20said%20while%20there%20may%20be%20other%20options%2C%20they%20would%20lead%20to%20increased%20costs%20or%20decreased%20motivation%20from%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDenholm%20said%20the%20CEO%20has%20worked%20incredibly%20hard%20over%20the%20last%20six%20years%20to%20lead%20the%20company%20to%20%26quot%3Btransformative%20growth.%26quot%3B%20While%20shareholders%20and%20customers%20have%20both%20benefited%2C%20Musk%20himself%20hasn't%20received%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRatifying%20the%20plan%20is%20the%20best%20option%2C%26quot%3B%20Denholm%20said.%20%26quot%3BClearly%2C%20if%20it%20doesn't%20pass%2C%20then%20there%20are%20other%20alternatives%2C%20but%20none%20of%20them%20are%20as%20good%20from%20a%20shareholder%20perspective%20as%20actually%20ratifying%20the%20plan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20no%20guarantee%20that%20the%20pay%20plan%20will%20survive%20even%20if%20shareholders%20%3Cem%3Edo%20%3C%2Fem%3Eratify%20it%20on%20June%2013.%20The%20Delaware%20court%20system%20could%20rule%20that%20it's%20still%20invalid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDenholm%20said%20if%20that%20were%20to%20happen%2C%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bdetrimental%26quot%3B%20to%20shareholders%2C%20which%20is%20another%20reason%20she%20said%20they%20were%20fighting%20so%20hard%20to%20get%20it%20ratified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%20that%20is%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20quite%20frankly%2C%20if%20you%20sit%20back%2C%20that%20is%20actually%20quite%20detrimental%20from%20a%20shareholder%20policy%20perspective.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShareholder%20votes%20have%20been%20pretty%20sacrosanct%20from%20a%20Delaware%20law%20perspective%2C%20from%20a%20corporate%20America%20perspective%2C%20from%20a%20legal%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvocates%20for%20and%20against%20ratifying%20Musk's%20pay%20package%20have%20been%20ramping%20up%20their%20arguments%20in%20recent%20weeks.%20Several%20investment%20firms%20urged%20shareholders%20to%20vote%20against%20it%2C%20most%20recently%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusks-55-billion-tesla-pay-gets-more-pushback-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEO%20of%20the%20California%20Public%20Employees'%20Retirement%20System.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Tesla's%20board%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-shareholder-billionaire-ron-baron-supports-elon-musk-pay-package-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprominent%20shareholders%20like%20Ron%20Baron%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20actively%20campaigning%20for%20its%20approval%2C%20arguing%20that%20it%20is%20fair%20and%20necessary%20to%20keep%20the%20CEO's%20focus%20on%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20does%20not%20earn%20a%20salary%20and%20his%20compensation%20relies%20on%20the%20company's%20performance%20with%20specific%20metrics%20defined%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-strikes-down-elon-musk-tesla-compensation-pay-package-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20executiv