att-and-arjun-kapoor-applaud-ranbir-kapoors-impressive-strength-training-skills-watch-video%2Farticleshow%2F110775368.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110775368.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERanbir%20Kapoor%20impresses%20fans%20with%20his%20dedication%20to%20fitness%20in%20a%20new%20strength%20training%20video%20for%20his%20upcoming%20film%20'Ramayana'%20directed%20by%20Nitish%20Tiwari.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Falia-bhatt-and-arjun-kapoor-applaud-ranbir-kapoors-impressive-strength-training-skills-watch-video%2Farticleshow%2F110775368.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BUnfortunate%26quot%3B%3A%20Kangana%20Ranaut's%20Mandi%20Rival%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20On%20Slap%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20Central%20Industrial%20Security%20Force%20(CISF)%20official%20allegedly%20slapped%20BJP%20MP%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20at%20the%20Chandigarh%20airport%20today%2C%20Congress%20leader%20and%20Ms%20Ranaut's%20poll%20rival%20in%20Mandi%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20called%20the%20incident%20%26quot%3Bunfortunate%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20for%20action%20against%20the%20official%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20unfortunate%20if%20these%20kinds%20of%20incidents%20are%20happening%20and%20should%20not%20happen%20to%20any%20person%2C%20particularly%20a%20woman.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20it%20has%20been%20done%20by%20a%20security%20person.%20We%20got%20to%20know%20that%20the%20security%20person%20had%20some%20grievances%20related%20to%20the%20farmer's%20protest%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20CISF%20to%20provide%20a%20peaceful%20atmosphere%20inside%20airports%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20a%20constitutional%20right%20and%20platform%20to%20bring%20up%20your%20grievances%20and%20issues.%20To%20assault%20a%20person%20like%20this%20is%20unfortunate.%20The%20government%20should%20take%20action%20against%20the%20person.%20Once%20you%20are%20in%20an%20airport%2C%20you%20are%20under%20the%20security%20protection%20of%20the%20CISF%2C%20and%20it%20is%20their%20duty%20to%20provide%20you%20with%20security%20and%20a%20peaceful%20atmosphere%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20CISF%20suspended%20the%20woman%20constable%2C%20who%20allegedly%20slapped%20actor%20and%20MP%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20inside%20Chandigarh%20airport%20during%20the%20security%20check.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20CISF%20officer%20confirmed%20the%20incident%20and%20said%20they%20are%20also%20in%20the%20process%20of%20filing%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20constable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20given%20a%20complaint%20to%20the%20local%20police%20station%20against%20the%20lady%20constable.%20She%20has%20been%20suspended%20with%20immediate%20effect%20and%20an%20inquiry%20has%20been%20ordered%20into%20the%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20around%203%3A30%20pm%20when%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20was%20on%20her%20way%20to%20board%20a%20flight%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20incident%2C%20Ms%20Ranaut%20in%20a%20video%20message%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20safe.%20I%20am%20perfectly%20fine.%20The%20incident%20took%20place%20during%20the%20security%20check.%20After%20I%20was%20done%20with%20the%20security%20check%2C%20a%20woman%20constable%20of%20the%20CISF%20waited%20for%20me%20to%20pass%20through%20the%20cabin.%20Later%2C%20she%20came%20from%20the%20side%2C%20hit%20me%20in%20the%20face%2C%20and%20started%20abusing%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20asked%20her%20why%20she%20did%20this%2C%20she%20said%20that%20she%20supported%20the%20farmers'%20protest.%20My%20question%20is%20how%20we%20end%20the%20growing%20extremism%20and%20terrorism%20in%20Punjab%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20CISF%20constable%20said%20her%20mother%20was%20among%20the%20farmers%20sitting%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20farm%20laws%2C%20which%20have%20now%20been%20repealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20(Kangana%20Ranaut)%20said%20that%20the%20farmers%20are%20sitting%20there%20for%20Rs%20100.%20Will%20she%20go%20and%20sit%20there%3F%20My%20mother%20was%20sitting%20there%20and%20protesting%20when%20she%20gave%20this%20statement...%26quot%3B%20the%20constable%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20protested%20for%2015%20months%20against%20the%20now-repealed%20farm%20laws%20and%20other%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKangana%20Ranaut%20defeated%20Congress%20candidate%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20from%20Himachal%20Pradesh's%20Mandi%20by%20a%20margin%20of%2074%2C755%20votes%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717697160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F4tvo2dp_vikramaditya-singh-kangana-ranaut_625x300_13_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funfortunate-kangana-ranauts-mandi-rival-vikramaditya-singh-on-slap-row-5833480%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20a%20CISF%20official%20allegedly%20slapped%20BJP%20MP%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20at%20the%20Chandigarh%20airport%20today%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20called%20the%20incident%20%26quot%3Bunfortunate%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20for%20action%20against%20the%20official%20concerned.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funfortunate-kangana-ranauts-mandi-rival-vikramaditya-singh-on-slap-row-5833480%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2