iatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110774061.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20upcoming%20film%20'Chandu%20Champion'%20starring%20Kartik%20Aaryan%20has%20garnered%20attention%20for%20the%20actor's%20transformation%20under%20director%20Kabir%20Khan's%20guidance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkabir-khan-says-kartik-aaryan-struggled-with-insomnia-before-chandu-champion-shoot%2Farticleshow%2F110774061.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Tsar%20Mangal'%20-%20Russia's%20Response%20To%20Ukraine's%20Drone%20Attacks%20On%20Tanks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDrones%20have%20dominated%20the%20battlefield%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20with%20cheap%2C%20unmanned%20ground%2Faerial%20vehicles%20taking%20out%20tanks%20worth%20several%20thousand%20dollars.%20The%20Russian%20forces%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20advanced%20in%20the%20world%2C%20are%20forced%20to%20strategize%20their%20operations%20to%20counter%20aerial%20threats%20from%20Ukraine%20-%20a%20much%20smaller%20force%20backed%20by%20NATO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20odd-looking%20big%20Russian%20tank%20was%20spotted%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine%20a%20few%20months%20ago.%20Covered%20with%20thick%20armoured%20sheets%2C%20modified%20T-72%20and%20T-90%20are%20Russia's%20response%20to%20Ukrainian%20drones.%20The%20Russians%20call%20them%20'Tsar%20Mangal'%2C%20and%20Ukrainians%20call%20them%20'Turtle%20Tanks'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EInnovation%20on%20the%20Battlefield%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20threat%20from%20drones%20became%20imminent.%20Cheap%20UAVs%20emerged%20as%20an%20economical%20option%20over%20the%20expensive%20American%20Javelin%20heat-seeking%20anti-tank%20guided%20missile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideos%20of%20tanks%20attacked%20by%20First%20Person%20View%20(FPV)%20drones%20started%20emerging%20last%20year%20when%20Russian%20T-72s%2C%20T-80s%2C%20and%20T-90s%20Main%20Battle%20Tanks%20became%20targets%20of%20these%20small%20armed%20aerial%20threats.%20Drones%20are%20used%20not%20just%20for%20limited-scale%20offensive%20operations%20but%20also%20for%20surveillance%20and%20guiding%20precision%20artillery%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Tsar%20Mangal'%20has%20a%20thick%20metal%20sheet%20protecting%20the%20roof%2C%20sides%2C%20and%20rear%20of%20a%20tank.%20Tsar%20Mangal%20has%20another%20layer%20of%20a%20metal%20grill%20protecting%20the%20metal%20sheets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3Ethis%20thing%20is%20huge.%20If%20it's%20role%20is%20purely%20plow%20the%20mines%2C%20it%20can%20work.%20However%20it's%20clear%20that%20it%20can't%20aim%20properly.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20tracks%20are%20still%20very%20vulnerable.%20however%20the%20FPVs%20are%20really%20hard%20to%20aim%20into%20the%20tracks%2C%20because%20of%20high%20chances%20of%20losing%20control%20over%20the%20drone%20at%20the%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJdIfLlPGzX%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FJdIfLlPGzX%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20%E2%9C%99%20Constantine%20%E2%9C%99%20(%40Teoyaomiquu)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTeoyaomiquu%2Fstatus%2F1787162849975873639%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spot%20between%20the%20hull%20and%20the%20turret%20is%20vulnerable%20because%20of%20the%20thin%20armour%20plating.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20rear%20of%20the%20tank%20is%20prone%20to%20attacks%20because%20of%20the%20engine%20compartment%20and%20armour%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%209%2C%20these%20tanks%20were%20seen%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20Krasnohorivka%2C%20a%20city%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine's%20Donetsk.%20A%20Ukrainian%20FPV%20drone%20attacked%20the%20tank%2C%20which%20was%20ultimately%20repelled.%20Reports%20say%20'Turtle%20Tanks'%20or%20'Tsar%20Mangal'%20have%20radio%20jammers%20for%20electronic%20warfare.%20Electronic%20jammers%20have%20proven%20effective%20in%20countering%20approaching%20FPV%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETsar%20Mangals%20are%20also%20used%20for%20mine-clearing%20operations%20for%20infantry%20fighting%20vehicles%20and%20infantry%20units%2C%20but%20the%20metal%20roof%20restricts%20the%20360-degree%20movement%20of%20the%20turret%2C%20limiting%20the%20manoeuvrability%20of%20the%20tank%20and%20reducing%20the%20visibility%20for%20the%20driver%20and%20the%20gunner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20Ukraine's%20Ministry%20of%20Defense%20shared%20a%20video%20of%20a%20drone%20attacking%20a%20'Turtle%20Tank'%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOccupiers%20made%20a%20'turtle'%20tank%20but%20forgot%20to%20close%20a%20hatch...drone%20pilots%20don't%20forgive%20such%20mistakes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOccupiers%20made%20a%20'turtle'%20tank%20but%20forgot%20to%20close%20a%20hatch...%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%F0%9F%87%BA%F0%9F%87%A6%20drone%20pilots%20don't%20forgive%20such%20mistakes.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%F0%9F%93%B9%3A%2093rd%20Mechanized%20Brigade%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FrHNxGbqgSk%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FrHNxGbqgSk%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Defense%20of%20Ukraine%20(%40DefenceU)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDefenceU%2Fstatus%2F1798401144693403853%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELessons%20From%20Ukraine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20Russia%20attached%20metal%20cages%20on%20top%20of%20tanks%20to%20protect%20their%20roof%20but%20proved%20ineffective.%20Also%20known%20as%20'Cope%20Cages'%2C%20the%20metal%20roofs%20were%20first%20used%20during%20the%20Armenia-Azerbaijan%20conflict.%20The%20lessons%20from%20different%20battlefields%20proliferated%2C%20and%20Israel%20attached%20'Cope%20Cages'%20to%20its%20Merkava%20IV%20tanks%20during%20its%20operation%20in%20Gaza.%20Even%20the%20Indian%20Army%20has%20installed%20metal%20roofs%20on%20its%20tanks%20located%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Black%20Raven%20battalion%20in%20Ukraine's%2093%20Mechanized%20Brigade%2C%20widely%20regarded%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20effective%20units%20in%20the%20forces%2C%20has%20carried%20out%20multiple%20drone%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20set%20a%20target%20of%20producing%20a%20million%20drones%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20as%20the%20war%20drags%20on%20for%20another%20year%20and%20a%20shortage%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20sets%20in%20amid%20a%20funding%20crunch%20from%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717689420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fmhak5ugo_russian-turtle-tank_625x300_06_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-ukraine-war-tsar-mangal-russia-innovates-to-counter-ukraines-drone-attacks-on-tanks-5831709%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Drones%20have%20dominated%20the%20battlefield%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20with%20cheap%2C%20unmanned%20ground%2Faerial%20vehicles%20taking%20out%20tanks%20worth%20several%20thousand%20dollars.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-ukraine-war-tsar-mangal-russia-innovates-to-counter-ukraines-drone-attacks-on-tanks-5831709%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-ukraine-war-tsar-mangal-russia-innovates-to-counter-ukraines-drone-attacks-on-tanks-5831709%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-ukraine-war-tsar-mangal-russia-innovates-to-counter-ukraines-drone-attacks-on-tanks-5831709%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22ti