eaders%20are%20in%20jail.%20The%20victory%20margin%20has%20reduced%20on%20all%20the%20seats%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20reporters%2C%20Mr%20Rai%20said%20there%20was%20disappointment%20among%20AAP%20workers%20after%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20but%20the%20party%20remained%20united%20even%20in%20difficult%20circumstances%20and%20put%20up%20a%20good%20fight%20against%20%26quot%3Bdictatorship%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asserted%20that%20the%20biggest%20advantage%20of%20the%20AAP-Congress%20alliance%20has%20been%20that%20the%20victory%20margins%20of%20the%20BJP%20candidates%20in%20Delhi%20have%20reduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20decided%20in%20the%20meeting%20that%2C%20on%20June%208%2C%20we%20will%20hold%20a%20meeting%20with%20councillors%20and%2C%20on%20June%2013%2C%20a%20meeting%20will%20be%20held%20with%20all%20party%20workers%20of%20Delhi.%20Since%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20is%20in%20jail%2C%20our%20struggle%20will%20continue%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20AAP%20Delhi%20convener%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20decided%20that%20all%20party%20MLAs%20will%20hold%20meetings%20with%20workers%20on%20Saturday%20and%20Sunday%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20development%20works%20since%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20has%20been%20lifted.%20The%20AAP-Congress%20combine%20failed%20to%20open%20its%20account%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20Delhi%2C%20with%20BJP%20effecting%20a%20clean%20sweep%20on%20all%20seven%20parliamentary%20seats%20for%20a%20record%20third%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717686780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fvu8dmsjo_arvind-kejriwal-rahul-gandhi-rahul-kejriwal-650_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-results-