n%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20indicates%20a%20steady%20climb%20since%202009%20when%20only%20315%20(58%20per%20cent)%20MPs%20were%20millionaires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20analysis%2C%20227%20(95%20per%20cent)%20of%20the%20BJP's%20240%20winning%20candidates%2C%2092%20(93%20per%20cent)%20of%20the%20Congress'%2099%2C%2021%20(95%20per%20cent)%20of%20the%20DMK's%2022%2C%2027%20(93%20per%20cent)%20of%20the%20TMC's%2029%20and%2034%20(92%20per%20cent)%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party's%2037%20candidates%20have%20declared%20assets%20worth%20more%20than%20Rs%201%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20winning%20candidates%20of%20the%20AAP%20(3)%2C%20the%20JDU%20(12)%20and%20the%20TDP%20(16)%20are%20millionaires%2C%20ADR%20data%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20analysis%20also%20delves%20into%20candidates'%20chances%20of%20winning%20based%20on%20their%20financial%20backgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20found%20that%20the%20probability%20of%20a%20millionaire%20candidate%20clinching%20victory%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20stood%20at%2019.6%20per%20cent%2C%20compared%20to%20a%20meagre%200.7%20per%20cent%20for%20candidates%20with%20assets%20less%20than%20a%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20analysis%20also%20provides%20a%20breakdown%20of%20wealth%20distribution%20among%20the%20winning%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20showed%20that%2042%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20candidates%20possess%20assets%20totalling%20Rs%2010%20crore%20and%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%2019%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20candidates%20fall%20within%20the%20bracket%20of%20Rs%205%20to%2010%20crore%2C%2032%20per%20cent%20hold%20assets%20ranging%20between%20Rs%201%20and%205%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20about%201%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20winning%20candidates%20have%20assets%20worth%20less%20than%20Rs%2020%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20major%20parties%2C%20the%20average%20assets%20per%20winning%20candidate%20vary%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TDP%20leads%20with%20an%20average%20of%20Rs%20442.26%20crore%20per%20winner%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20BJP%20with%20Rs%2050.04%20crore%2C%20the%20DMK%20with%20Rs%2031.22%20crore%2C%20the%20Congress%20with%20Rs%2022.93%20crore%2C%20TMC%20with%20Rs%2017.98%20crore%20and%20SP%20with%20Rs%2015.24%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20analysis%20also%20highlights%20disparities%20within%20the%20financial%20profiles%20of%20winning%20candidates.%20While%20some%20boast%20of%20substantial%20assets%2C%20others%20have%20relatively%20low%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20BJP's%20Jyotirmay%20Singh%20Mahato%20from%20West%20Bengal's%20Purulia%20has%20declared%20assets%20totalling%20a%20mere%20Rs%205%20lakh.%20Similarly%2C%20TMC's%20Mitali%20Bag%20from%20West%20Bengal's%20Arambag%20holds%20assets%20worth%20Rs%207%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssets%20of%20SP's%20Priya%20Saroj%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Machhlishahr%20are%20valued%20at%20Rs%2011%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20analysis%20identifies%20candidates%20with%20high%20liabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDP's%20Pemmasani%20tops%20the%20list%20with%20liabilities%20exceeding%20Rs%201%2C038%20crore.%20DMK's%20S%20Jagathratchakan%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Arakkonam%20has%20liabilities%20worth%20Rs%20649%20crore%20and%20TDP's%20Prabhakar%20Reddy%20Vemireddy%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Nellore%20has%20liabilities%20worth%20Rs%20197%20crore.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717682160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F78c91mcc_lok-sabha-generic-ians_625x300_06_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F93-of-lok-sabha-poll-winners-are-millionaires-report-5830810%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20staggering%2093%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20candidates%20who%2