woman%20was%20%26quot%3Bavailable%20for%20Rs%20100%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20had%20triggered%20a%20much-talked-about%20exchange%20on%20X%20between%20her%20and%20singer-actor%20Diljeet%20Dosanjh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERihanna%20Reaction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20in%20February%202021%2C%20reacting%20to%20support%20for%20the%20protests%20by%20international%20pop%20sensation%20Rihanna%2C%20Ms%20Ranaut%20had%20called%20the%20agitators%20%26quot%3Bterrorists%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20divide%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20a%20post%20on%20X%20by%20Rihanna%2C%20Ms%20Ranaut%20had%20called%20the%20singer%20a%20%26quot%3Bfool%26quot%3B%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20is%20talking%20about%20it%20because%20they%20are%20not%20farmers%20they%20are%20terrorists%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20divide%20India%2C%20so%20that%20China%20can%20take%20over%20our%20vulnerable%20broken%20nation%20and%20make%20it%20a%20Chinese%20colony%20much%20like%20USA...%20Sit%20down%20you%20fool%2C%20we%20are%20not%20selling%20our%20nation%20like%20you%20dummies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20an%20X%20user%20had%20pointed%20to%20a%202019%20tweet%20by%20Ms%20Ranaut%20in%20which%20she%20had%20appeared%20to%20express%20her%20appreciation%20for%20Rihanna%2C%20the%20actor%20had%20responded%20with%20a%20post%20bordering%20on%20the%20abusive%20in%20which%20she%20said%20she%20had%20taken%20over%20the%20account%20only%20recently%20and%20did%20not%20listen%20to%20English%20music%20much.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EOye%20tattu%3C%2Fem%3E%20I%20took%20over%20my%20account%20in%20August%20last%20year%20before%20that%20it%20was%20a%20team%20fan%20page%2C%20%3Cem%3Emujhe%20na%20pop%20music%20samajh%20aata%20hai%20nahi%20main%20English%20gaane%20zyaada%20sunti%20hoon%3C%2Fem%3E%20(I%20don't%20understand%20pop%20music%20nor%20do%20I%20listen%20to%20English%20songs%20much)%20.%20%3Cem%3ESoja%20aab%20ho%20