%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Industrial%20Security%20Force%20(CISF)%20constable%20who%20slapped%20the%20new%20MP%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Kulwinder%20Kaur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20slapping%20Ms%20Ranaut%2C%20the%20paramilitary%20constable%20allegedly%20told%20the%20actor-turned-MP%20it%20was%20for%20%26quot%3Bdisrespecting%20farmers%26quot%3B%2C%20alluding%20to%20the%2015-month-long%20protest%20by%20farmers%20against%20the%20(now%20scrapped)%20farm%20laws%20and%20other%20issues%20including%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20of%20minimum%20support%20price%20in%202020-21.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMobile%20footage%20shows%20Ms%20Ranaut%20being%20escorted%20by%20a%20ring%20of%20security%20officers%20towards%20the%20security%20check-in%2C%20where%20she%20is%20seen%20talking%20to%20some%20CISF%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CISF%20Commandant%20has%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20and%20is%20questioning%20the%20constable%2C%20sources%20said.%20One%20of%20her%20aides%20has%20also%20informed%20the%20local%20police%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarmers%20Protest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20had%20blocked%20her%20convoy%20in%20Chandigarh%20during%20the%20election%20campaign%20while%20Ms%20Ranaut%20was%20going%20towards%20Mandi.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20February%202021%2C%20international%20pop%20star%20Rihanna%20posted%20on%20X%20(then%20Twitter)%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Centre%20over%20the%20farmers'%20protest%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20aren't%20we%20talking%20about%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20Ms%20Ranaut%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20is%20talking%20about%20it%20because%20they%20are%20not%20farmers%2C%20they%20are%20terrorists%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20divide%20India%2C%20so%20that%20China%20can%20take%20over%20our%20vulnerable%20broken%20nation%20and%20make%20it%20a%20Chinese%20colony%20much%20like%20the%20USA...%20Sit%20down%20you%20fool%2C%20we%20are%20not%20selling%20our%20nation