0I%20realized%20that%20I%20was%20kind%20of%20fast%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20become%20just%20a%20little%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20sort%20of%20a%20challenge%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20aimed%20for%20like%20150%20WPM%2C%20and%20then%20once%20I%20hit%20150%2C%20I%20aimed%20for%20160-all%20the%20way%20up%20to%20like%20200.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20from%20there%2C%20I%20think%20I%20stopped%20for%20a%20while.%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'OK%2C%20I%20hit%20my%20goal.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20attributes%20his%20success%20to%20a%20combination%20of%20factors%2C%20including%20frequent%20participation%20in%20gaming%20experiences%20that%20emphasize%20typing%20proficiency%20and%20a%20personal%20commitment%20to%20exceeding%20his%20own%20limitations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERocket%20relied%20on%20two%20free%20online%20typing%20platforms%20to%20climb%20from%20200%20WPM%20all%20the%20way%20up%20to%20304.76.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20my%20practice%20is%20on%20these%20two%20websites%2C%20Monkeytype%20and%20Typeracer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20every%20day%20I%20would%20load%20(Monkeytype)%20up%20for%20maybe%20like%2015%2C%2030%20minutes%2C%20and%20I%20just%20type%2C%20go%20ham%2C%20and%20I'd%20just%20keep%20doing%20it%20and%20then%20I'd%20get%20faster%2C%26quot%3B%20Rocket%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20the%2060-second%20world%20record%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20adds.%20%26quot%3BI%20also%20have%20the%2015-second%20one.%20I%20have%20other%20ones%2C%20too%2C%20but%20people%20don't%20really%20care%20about%20those.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20more%20practice%20can%20definitely%20increase%20his%20speed.%20%26quot%3BI%20definitely%20think%20it%20is%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Rocket%2C%20on%20pushing%20past%20the%20305%20WPM%20barrier.%20%26quot%3BI%20definitely%20know%20that%20I%20am%20capable%20of%20breaking%20my%20record.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E