seats%20between%20them%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20getting%2023%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20party%2018.%20The%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20BJP's%20oldest%20allies%2C%20also%20contested%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20Maharashtra%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20it%20later%20that%20year%2C%20but%20fell%20out%20and%20left%20the%20NDA%20over%20disagreements%20regarding%20the%20chief%20minister's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUddhav%20Thackeray%20was%20then%20sworn%20in%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadicoalition%20with%20the%20NCP%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThings%20began%20to%20change%20drastically%20three%20years%20later%2C%20when%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Eknath%20Shinde%20-%20%C2%A0alleged%20to%20have%20been%20egged%20on%20by%20the%20BJP%20-%20split%20the%20party%20and%20went%20back%20to%20the%20NDA%2C%20claiming%20that%20Mr%20Thackeray%20had%20gone%20against%20the%20mandate%20given%20to%20the%20alliance%20in%202019.%20With%20his%20government's%20majority%20gone%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20stepped%20down%20and%20Mr%20Shinde%20took%20oath%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20with%20the%20BJP's%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20as%20his%20deputy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20was%20split%20a%20year%20later%20and%20Mr%20Shinde%20got%20his%20second%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20in%20Ajit%20Pawar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlot%20Changes%20Again%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20was%2C%20thus%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20unusual%20in%20Maharashtra's%20history%2C%20with%20two%20Shiv%20Senas%20and%20two%20NCPs%20-%20under%20very%20similar%20but%20different%20names%20-%20pitted%20against%20each%20other.%20The%20Shinde%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20factions%20were%20supported%20by%20the%20BJP%20while%20the%20Thackeray%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20groups%20were%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20the%20Shinde%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20groups%20were%20recognised%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Breal%26quot%3B%20parties%20and%20allotted%20the%20party%20symbols%20came%20as%20another%20blow%20to%20the%20Thackeray%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20factions%2C%20for%20whom%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20became%20a%20matter%20of%20prestige%20as%20well%20as%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20Sena-BJP-NCP%20alliance%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Mahayuti%2C%20exuded%20confidence%20that%20it%20would%20manage%20to%20win%20most%20seats.%20The%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20ended%20up%20being%20reduced%20to%20nine%20from%2023%2C%20while%20Team%20Shinde%20got%20seven%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20only%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Congress-Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)-NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20coalition%2C%20won%2030%20of%20the%20state's%2048%20constituencies.%20The%20Congress%20emerged%20as%20the%20largest%20party%2C%20winning%2013%2C%20while%20Team%20Uddhav%20got%20nine%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20party%20won%20eight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717675920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fmg6p0jn_uddhav-thackeray-1200_625x300_20_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-results-2024-on-rumours-of-going-back-to-the-nda-team-uddhav-says-5831654%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rubbishing%20rumours%2C%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20has%20said%20that%20it%20is%20going%20to%20remain%20with%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20will%20not%20switch%20back%20to%20the%20NDA.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-results-2024-on-rumours-of-going-back-to-the-nda-team-uddhav-says-5831654%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-results-2024-on-rumours