o%20assess%20how%20much%20solar%20energy%20can%20be%20captured%20in%20a%20specific%20place.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20if%20you%20live%20on%2C%20say%2C%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20a%2020-storey%20building%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20bringing%20the%20cable%20(wire)%20down%20from%20the%20terrace%20would%20be%20enormous.%20The%20add-ons%20could%20run%20into%20an%20additional%20Rs%201%20lakh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2211%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20you%20can%20opt%20for%20balconies%20which%20can%20minimise%20the%20cabling%20cost%20as%20the%20whole%20system%20would%20be%20drawn%20to%20your%20house%20including%20the%20net%20metre.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20viable%20proposition%20for%20apartment%20owners%20and%20tenants%20with%20rental%20agreements%20for%2010%20or%2015%20years.%20Tenants%20cannot%20remove%20the%20setup%20to%20take%20it%20somewhere%20else%20because%20it%20will%20again%20involve%20paperwork%20and%20installation%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2212%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20assume%20the%20monthly%20power%20expenses%20to%20be%20Rs%202%2C500%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20installation%20and%20inverter%20(with%20a%2010-year%20warranty)%20to%20be%20Rs%201.5%20lakh.%20So%2C%20for%20a%2015-year%20contract%2C%20the%20return%20on%20investment%20will%20be%20generated%20only%20after%20five%20years%20and%20residents%20can%20avail%20of%20eight%20years%20of%20free%20electricity%20provided%20the%20inverter%20lasts%20for%20say%2013%20years.%20Later%20on%2C%20the%20landlord%20will%20incur%20the%20capital%20cost%20for%20the%20new%20inverter.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2213%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHighlighting%20the%20challenges%20on%20the%20terrace%20and%20balconies%2C%20Harish%20mentions%20that%20residents%20will%20have%20to%20bear%20metre%20and%20wiring%20expenses%20that%20can%20go%20up%20to%20R