0the%20perfect%20opportunity%20to%20experiment%20and%20create%20these%20popsicles.%20In%20an%20attempt%20to%20provide%20a%20healthier%20alternative%20to%20ice-cream%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20chefs%20to%20create%20recipes%20made%20out%20of%20fruits.%20He%20also%20got%20his%20team%20ready.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20importantly%2C%20he%20worked%20on%20developing%20a%20popsicle%20machine%20that%20would%20freeze%20them%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20minutes.%20Months%20of%20trials%20and%20four%20prototypes%20later%2C%20he%20had%20the%20perfect%20machine%20ready%2C%20which%20%E2%80%9Cfreezes%20a%20popsicle%20within%207%20to%208%20minutes%20in%20front%20of%20you%20with%20a%20temperature%20of%20minus%2031%20degrees%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20experience%20in%20the%20franchising%20business%20and%20QSR%20(Quick%20Service%20Restaurant)%20led%20him%20to%20develop%20a%20string%20of%20processes%20that%20can%20easily%20be%20replicated%20across%20stores.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvesting%20Rs%2070%20lakh%20of%20his%20savings%2C%20Gagan%20started%20the%20first%20Scuzo%20Ice-O-Magic%20store%20in%20Netaji%20Subhash%20Place%2C%20Pitampura%2C%20New%20Delhi%20in%20November%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderstanding%20that%20just%20popsicles%20might%20not%20work%2C%20he%20also%20developed%20gelato%2C%20an%20Italian%20frozen%20dessert%2C%20in%20a%20manufacturing%20unit.%20In%20order%20to%20cater%20to%20a%20wider%20audience%2C%20the%20dessert%20cafe%20serves%20waffles%2C%20milkshakes%2C%20hot%20beverages%2C%20sundaes%20in%20addition%20to%20popsicles%20and%20gelato.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20store%20had%20a%20great%20response%2C%20according%20to%20the%20founder%2C%20with%20people%20enquiring%20for%20franchisees%20in%20the%20first%20three%20months%20itself.%20The%20first%20franchise%20store%20was%20opened%20in%20March%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Scuzo%20has%2030%20stores%20in%2025%20cities%20across%20the%20country%2C%20of%20which%2027%20are%20franchisees%20and%203%20are%20company-owned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273408%2Fskippi-ice-popsicles-ravi-anuja-kabra-win-million-shark-tank%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epopsicles%20start%20at%20Rs%2065%20%3C%2Fa%3Ea%20piece%20while%20the%20gelato%20starts%20at%20Rs%20110.%20Their%20bestseller%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3Echatpata%20jamun%20%3C%2Fem%3Epopsicle%3Cem%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3EGagan%20shares%20that%20the%20popsicles%20are%20made%20from%20%E2%80%98100%20percent%20fruit%E2%80%99.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20are%20served%20with%20edible%20rice%20straws.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20has%20been%20far%20from%20smooth%20as%20the%20second%20wave%20of%20COVID-19%20brought%20a%20halt%20to%20his%20growth.%20The%20first%20store%2C%20which%20was%20in%20a%20mall%2C%20had%20to%20be%20shut%20down%20and%20moved%20to%20Noida.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelivery%20too%2C%20is%20a%20big%20challenge%2C%20according%20to%20Gagan.%20Most%20food%20delivery%20companies%20don%E2%80%99t%20provide%20the%20cooling%20pouch%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20just%205%20percent%20of%20sales%20from%20online%20channels.%20To%20combat%20this%2C%20Gagan%20hopes%20to%20start%20his%20own%20delivery%20service%20to%20ensure%20proper%20delivery%20of%20the%20popsicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20was%20his%20happiest%20moment%3F%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20told%20me%20that%20he%20was%20very%20proud%20of%20me%20because%20I%20achieved%20so%20much%20without%20taking%20a%20single%20rupee%20from%20him.%20He%20passed%20away%20in%202021%2C%20but%20he%20got%20to%20see%20all%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Image%20Courtesy%3A%20Gagan%20Anand%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717422447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-03-at-18.45.33-min-1717420586.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351903%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gagan%20Anand%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20when%20he%20was%2017%20and%20picked%20up%20a%20job%20at%20Pizza%20Hut.%20Starting%20with%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%201500%2C%20he%20now%20runs%20a%20dessert%20cafe%20called%20Scuzo%20Ice-O-Magic%2C%20which%20serves%20popsicles%20and%20gelato.%20Here's%20a%20look%20at%20his%20entrepreneurial%20journey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F351903%2Fice-popsicle-startup-scuzo-chai-delhi-ncr-fruit-gelatos-live-dessert-cafe-gagan-anand%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Doctor%20Returned%20From%20The%20UK%20%26amp%3B%20Inspired%202.5%20Million%20Indians%20to%20Become%20Future%20Organ%20Donors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20year%20was%201996.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sunil%20Shroff%E2%80%99s%20voice%20softens%20as%20he%20narrates%20a%20life%20changing%20incident%20that%20happened%20back%20then.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2070-year-old%20urologist%20and%20renal%20transplant%20surgeon%20was%20about%20to%20perform%20one%20of%20his%20first%20few%20%E2%80%98deceased%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310277%2Fabhinav-pangtey-shares-myths-about-organ-donation-india-world-transplant-games%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorgan%20donations%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20on%20a%2012-year-old%20boy%20who%20died%20of%20a%20cobra%20bite.%20The%20surgery%20was%20scheduled%20at%20the%20Sri%20Ramachandra%20Medical%20College%20and%20Research%20Institute%20(SRMC%20%26amp%3B%20RI)%20in%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shroff%20explains%20how%20after%20the%20initial%20treatment%20failed%2C%20the%20young%20child%20was%20declared%20brain%20dead%20at%20the%20hospital.%20The%20doctors%20there%20waited%20for%20five%20days%20for%20him%20to%20recover%2C%20but%20he%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20did%20not.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20hesitantly%20approached%20the%20grief-stricken%20father%20and%20asked%20him%20whether%20he%20would%20donate%20the%20boy%E2%80%99s%20organs%2C%20which%20he%20consented%20to.%20Two%20kidneys%2C%20a%20heart%20and%20two%20corneas%20were%20harvested%20and%20transplanted%20in%20five%20individuals%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F139488%2Forgan-donation-india-youth-awareness-increase%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egiving%20them%20the%20gift%20of%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20made%20the%20hospital%20famous%20as%20it%20was%20only%20the%20fourth%20hospital%20to%20perform%20such%20a%20procedure%20in%20the%20country.%20This%20unique%20case%20of%20organ%20donation%20from%20a%20snake%20bite%20victim%20was%20published%20in%20an%20international%20journal%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%20began%20Dr%20Shroff%E2%80%99s%20dedicated%20mission%20to%20promote%20deceased%20organ%20donation%20and%20transplantation%20in%20India.%20To%20facilitate%20his%20mission%2C%20he%20established%20the%20not-for-profit%20MOHAN%20(Multi%20Organ%20Harvesting%20Aid%20Network)%20Foundation%20in%201997.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20Dr%20Shroff%20is%20a%20senior%20consultant%20of%20urology%20and%20transplantation%20at%20the%20Madras%20Medical%20Mission%20Hospital%20in%20Chennai.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20managing%20trustee%20of%20MOHAN%20Foundation.%20Notably%2C%20he%20was%20the%20first%20Indian%20surgeon%20to%20perform%20a%20successful%20kidney%20transplant%20on%20an%20HIV%20positive%20patient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20with%20the%20MOHAN%20Foundation%2C%2010%20lakh%20people%20in%20India%20suffer%20from%20end-stage%20organ%20failure%20every%20year.%20Only%2016%2C041%20receive%20live-saving%20organs%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%