ink%20rock%20salt%20from%20Pakistan%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20spices%20and%20herbs%20from%201%2C000%20small%20farmers%20in%20Uttarakhand.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandeep%20now%20knew%20what%20needed%20to%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202013%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20commercialise%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310963%2Fsashi-bahuguna-raturi-uttarakhand-pisyu-loon-salt-namakwali-video%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflavoured%20salt%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20provide%20employment%20to%20rural%20women.%20Along%20with%20his%20childhood%20friends%20Sourabh%20Pant%20and%20Yogendra%20Singh%2C%20he%20launched%20HimFla%20%E2%80%93%20short%20for%20Himalayan%20Flavours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20inception%20of%20a%20multi-crore%20business%20with%20just%20Rs%20160%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20uniqueness%20of%20the%20flavoured%20salt%2C%20Sandeep%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20days%2C%20kitchens%20are%20mostly%20modular%3B%20traditional%20%3Cem%3Esilbattas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehave%20been%20replaced%20by%20grinders%20and%20mixers.%20Although%20electronic%20machines%20have%20made%20our%20lives%20easier%2C%20the%20taste%20achieved%20through%20grinding%20in%20%3Cem%3Esilbattas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecan%E2%80%99t%20be%20got%20through%20modern%20equipment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20a%20%3Cem%3Esilbatta%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20salt%20is%20pounded%20without%20any%20heat.%20This%20keeps%20the%20natural%20taste%20and%20flavours%20intact.%20In%20a%20grinder%2C%20the%20food%20is%20just%20cut%20into%20very%20fine%20pieces%20and%20not%20pounded%20to%20be%20properly%20mixed.%20When%20you%20use%20a%20%3Cem%3Esilbatta%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20actually%20blending%20all%20the%20oils%20of%20the%20herbs%20and%20spices%20together%20to%20enhance%20the%20flavours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3